w-2016-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecloned%20sheep%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0across%20state%20lines.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20retail%20value%20of%20the%20transported%20animals%20is%20%24250%2C000%20to%20%24550%2C000%2C%20per%20court%20documents.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20hybrid%20offspring%20were%20sold%20to%20game%20farms%2C%20possibly%20for%20hunting.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAn%2080-year-old%20Montana%20rancher%2C%20Arthur%20%26quot%3BJack%26quot%3B%20Schubarth%2C%20had%20a%20lucrative%20business%20going%20until%20authorities%20got%20wind%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20last%20five%20years%2C%20or%20so%2C%20Schubarth%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faustralian-farmers-giving-sheep-away-culling-prices-plummet-exports-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eselling%20sheep%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20dollars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20nothing%20illegal%20about%20selling%20sheep%20for%20exorbitant%20prices%20%E2%80%94%20unless%20those%20animals%20are%20Marco%20Polo%20argali%20sheep%2C%20or%20in%20Schubarth's%20case%2C%20hybrids%20of%20Marco%20Polo%20argali%20sheep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMarco%20Polo%20argali%20sheep%20are%20native%20to%20central%20Asia%20and%20are%20considered%20threatened%20under%20the%20US%20Endangered%20Species%20Act.%20Montana%20law%20prohibits%20importing%2C%20possessing%2C%20and%20selling%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20Schubarth%20pleaded%20guilty%20to%20charges%20in%20a%20scheme%20that%20involved%20all%20three.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20sentencing%20is%20scheduled%20for%20July%20and%20he%20faces%20up%20to%20five%20years%20in%20prison%20and%20a%20fine%20of%20up%20to%20%24250%2C000%20for%20each%20of%20the%20two%20felony%20counts%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20US%20has%20wildlife%20protection%20laws%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20all%20started%20in%202013%20when%20an%20unnamed%20party%20illegally%20imported%20Marco%20Polo%20argali%20sheep%20parts%20to%20the%20US%20from%20