%20relating%20to%20Cohen's%20federal%20prosecution.%20The%20defense%20has%20only%20dragged%20its%20feet%20in%20seeking%20the%20same%20evidence%2C%20prosecutors%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20his%20own%20filing%2C%20Trump%20attorney%20Todd%20Blanche%20countered%20that%20Bragg's%20lawyers%20%26quot%3Bhave%20engaged%20in%20widespread%20misconduct%26quot%3B%20by%20attempting%20to%20%26quot%3Bsuppress%26quot%3B%20the%20federal%20evidence%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20improve%20their%20chances%20at%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20People%20should%20have%20collected%20all%20of%20these%20documents%20long%20ago%2C%26quot%3B%20Blanche%20claimed%20in%20his%20motion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInstead%2C%20they%20collected%20some%20materials%20but%20left%20others%20with%20the%20federal%20authorities%2C%20in%20the%20hope%20that%20President%C2%A0Trump%C2%A0would%20never%20get%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20his%20motion%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20sides%20appear%20to%20agree%20that%20the%20delay%20was%20triggered%20by%20some%2073%2C000%20pages%20of%20records%20%E2%80%94%20sought%20for%20months%20by%20both%20the%20DA's%20office%20and%20the%20defense%20%E2%80%94%20that%20have%20been%20turned%20over%20in%20tranches%20throughout%20this%20month%20by%20the%20US%20Attorney's%20Office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20that%20massive%20evidence%20dump%2C%20some%2031%2C000%20pages%20were%20turned%20over%20only%20Wednesday%2C%20Manhattan%20Assistant%20District%20Attorney%20Matthew%20Colangelo%20wrote%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20trial%20judge%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20pages%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20turned%20over%20by%20federal%20prosecutors%20next%20week%2C%20Colangelo%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20each%20side%20is%20accusing%20the%20other%20of%20footdragging%20in%20pursuing%20this%20last-minute%20evidence%2C%20which%20includes%20federal%20grand%20jury%20minutes%2C%20tapes%2C%20witness%20lists%20and%20other%20documents%20relating%20to%20Cohen%20%E2%80%94%20the%20former%20Trump%20fi