eaked-documents-ukrainian-air-defense.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emade%20headlines%20in%20April%202023%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFrederico%20Borsari%2C%20a%20defense%20expert%20at%20the%20Center%20for%20European%20Policy%20Analysis%20(CEPA)%2C%20told%20Insider%20the%20potential%20delivery%20of%20Greek%20S-300s%20%26quot%3Bacquires%20even%20more%20relevance%20considering%20the%20recent%20destruction%20of%20at%20least%20one%20M903%20launcher%20for%20the%20Patriot%20PAC-2%20air%20defense%20system%20by%20a%20Russian%20Iskander-M%20ballistic%20missile.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20United%20States%2C%20Germany%2C%20and%20the%20Netherlands%20supplied%20Ukraine%20with%20Patriot%20missiles%2C%20which%20had%20success%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-patriot-defense-system-unstoppable-russian-hypersonic-kinzhal-missile-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eshooting%20down%20Russian%20Kinzhal%20hypersonic%20missiles%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20several%20Russian%20military%20aircraft.%20Ukraine%20may%20have%20lost%20at%20least%20one%20Patriot%20launcher%20%E2%80%94%20not%20an%20entire%20system%20%E2%80%94%20in%20a%20Russian%20Iskander%20missile%20strike%20outside%20the%20eastern%20city%20of%20Pokrovsk%20on%20Mar.%209%3B%20this%20claim%20could%20not%20be%20independently%20confirmed.%20The%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmod_russia%2F36445%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ERussian%20defense%20ministry%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftass.com%2Fdefense%2F1757417%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eidentified%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20destroyed%20launcher%20as%20a%20Ukrainian%20S-300.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20were%20already%20credible%20theories%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-destroyed-key-russia-aircraft-maybe-used-patriot-missiles-experts-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ein%20January%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20Ukraine%20had%20relocated%20Patriots%20near%20the%20front%20lines%2C%20enabling%20them%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-says-it-downed-over-dozen-russian-planes-this-month-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eshoot%20down%20a%20dozen%20Russian%20fighter%20jets%20in%20February%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThe%20loss%20showed%20the%20consequences%20of%20not%20changing%20location%20frequently%20in%20the%20context%20of%20a%20much%20faster%20detection-engagement%20cycle%20enabled%20by%20ubiquitous%20drones%20integrated%20with%20fire%20capabilities%20as%20part%20of%20multi-level%20reconnaissance-strike%20complexes%2C%26quot%3B%20Borsari%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERussia%20attacked%20Ukraine's%20Odesa%20on%20Mar.%206%20while%20Greek%20Prime%20Minister%20Kyriakos%20Mitsotakis%20was%20visiting.%20A%20Russian%20missile%20exploded%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2024%2F03%2F06%2Feurope%2Frussia-missile-odesa-greece-russia-zelensky-intl%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ea%20mere%20500%20meters%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20from%20the%20convoy%20he%20was%20traveling%20in%20with%20Ukrainian%20Prime%20Minister%20Volodymyr%20Zelensky.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Odesa%20military%20strike%20was%20a%20personal%20shock%20for%20the%20Greek%20delegation%20visiting%20Ukraine%2C%26quot%3B%20Tzogopoulos%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20strategic%20decisions%20are%20not%20made%20on%20the%20grounds%20of%20personal%20experiences.%20Greece%20values%20its%20strategic%20relationship%20with%20the%20US%2C%20which%20is%20how%20the%20new%20tone%20of%20the%20media%20discussion%20about%20sending%20S-300s%20to%20Ukraine%20could%20be%20better%20framed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20Ukraine's%20capacity%20to%20continue%20fighting%20against%20Russia's%20invasion%20depends%20on%20many%20factors%2C%20Tzogopoulos%20pointed%20out%20that%20Greece's%20contribution%20could%20%26quot%3Bacquire%20new%20significance%26quot%3B%20if%20it%20transfers%20S-300s.%20Greece%20is%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgreekcitytimes.com%2F2022%2F03%2F14%2Fnato-explores-sending-ukraine-more-advanced-weapons%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eestimated%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20have%2032%20launchers%20and%20up%20to%20175%20missiles%20it%20could%20provide.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BImportant%20as%20it%20will%20be%2C%20such%20a%20decision%20can%20hardly%20be%20considered%20a%20game%20changer%2C%20though%2C%26quot%3B%20Tzogopoulos%20said.%20%26quot%3BUkraine%20already%20possesses%20that%20type%20of%20long-range%20surface-to-air%20system%20and%20will%20benefit%20by%20seeing%20the%20number%20of%20its%20batteries%20increase%20%E2%80%94%20not%20by%20acquiring%20a%20new%20type%20of%20weapon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlthough%20it%20certainly%20won't%20be%20a%20new%20capability%2C%20the%20particular%20S-300%20variant%20in%20Greece's%20possession%20could%20benefit%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBorsari%20of%20CEPA%20pointed%20out%20that%20Greece's%20S-300PMU-1%20variant%20is%20more%20capable%20than%20the%20S-300PS%20variant%20typically%20operated%20by%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThe%20S-300PMU-1%20relies%20on%20an%20upgraded%20battery's%20radar%20module%20with%20improved%20detection%2C%20tracking%2C%20and%20engagement%20capabilities%20(comprising%20the%2030N6E%20fire%20control%20radar%20and%2076N6E%20low-level%20early%20warning%2Facquisition%20radar%20%E2%80%94%20and%20potentially%20the%20battalion-level%2064N6E%20acquisition%20radar)%20and%20can%20fire%20the%2048N6E%20missile%20besides%20the%20usual%205V55%20series%2C%26quot%3B%20Borsari%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBorsari%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20latter%20has%20better%20kinematics%2C%20a%20longer%20range%20(up%20to%20150%20km)%2C%20and%20a%20larger%20warhead.%20It%20uses%20a%20combination%20of%20radio%20command%20guidance%20and%20semi-active%20radar%20homing%20guidance%20and%20is%20effective%20against%20a%20wide%20target%20set%2C%20from%20cruise%20missiles%20and%20fast%20jets%20to%20ballistic-type%20threats.%26quot%3B%20Kinematics%20refer%20to%20the%20flight%20paths%20that%20can%20be%20flown%20to%20intercept%20an%20incoming%20missile%20or%20aircraft.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGiven%20the%20%26quot%3Battrition%20suffered%26quot%3B%20by%20Ukrainian%20S-300%20systems%20so%20far%20in%20this%20war%2C%20Borsari%20believes%20that%20even%20a%20%26quot%3Blimited%20number%20of%20launchers%26quot%3B%20could%20be%20%26quot%3Bvery%20useful%26quot%3B%20for%20Kyiv.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BIf%20radars%20and%20spare%20interceptors%20are%20also%20included%20in%20the%20package%2C%20that%20would%20be%20a%20significant%20addition%20to%20Ukraine's%20air%20and%20missile%20defense%2C%26quot%3B%20Borsari%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgreeces-s300-missiles-ukraine-air-defenses-at-a-critical-moment-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710447852000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65f35cc8857f90b71522bfda%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgreeces-s300-missiles-ukraine-air-defenses-at-a-critical-moment-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20turnabout%20on%20air%20defense%20missiles%20comes%20after%20a%20Russian%20missile%20struck%20near%20Greece's