%20data%20was%20released%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20earlier%20this%20week%2C%20asked%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20(SBI)%20to%20furnish%20all%20details%20of%20those%20who%20had%20purchased%20and%20those%20who%20had%20encashed%20anonymous%20electoral%20bonds%20since%202019.%20It%20had%20also%20asked%20the%20Election%20Commission%20to%20publish%20the%20data%20on%20its%20website%20by%20March%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20data%2C%20uploaded%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission%2C%20includes%20two%20documents%20%E2%80%93%20one%20a%20datewise%20list%20of%20purchases%20by%20companies%2C%20and%20the%20other%20a%20datewise%20list%20of%20deposits%20by%20political%20parties%20that%20have%20encashed%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EFuture%20Gaming%3A%20Under%20the%20ED%E2%80%99s%20lens%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFuture%20Gaming%20and%20Hotel%20Services%20PR%20has%20donated%20Rs%201%2C368%20crore%20between%20October%2021%2C%202020%20and%20January%209%2C%202024%2C%20all%20in%20denominations%20of%20Rs%201%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECoimbatore-based%20Future%20Gaming%20is%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20biggest%20lottery%20companies%20and%20its%20founder%20Santiago%20Martin%2C%20styles%20himself%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Clottery%20king.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20July%2023%2C%202019%2C%20the%20ED%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fchennai%2Fed-attaches-rs-120-crore-assets-of-martin-in-tamil-nadu-lottery-scam%2Farticleshow%2F70338379.cms%5C%22%3E%20attached%20assets%20worth%20Rs%20120%20crore%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20an%20alleged%20money%20laundering%20scam%2C%20where%20he%20was%20accused%20of%20inflating%20prize%20money%20and%20amassing%20property%20from%20unaccounted%20cash%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20also%20said%20that%20a%20few%20months%20earlier%2C%20the%20ED%20had%20searched%20over%2070%20premises%20associated%20with%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%