d%20much%20less%20pickup%20than%20OpenAI's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-gptbot-ccbot-more-companies-block-ai-web-crawlers-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGPTBot%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20hovering%20at%20around%2032%25%20of%20the%20top%201%2C000%20websites.%20CCBot%2C%20offered%20by%20Common%20Crawl%2C%20also%20has%20been%20switched%20on%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBI%20asked%20Originality.ai%20CEO%20Jonathan%20Gillham%20why%20Google-Extended%20is%20being%20used%20less%20than%20other%20AI%20training%20data-blockers.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20if%20Google%20rolls%20out%20a%20generative%20AI%20search%20engine%20to%20the%20wider%20public%2C%20there's%20a%20risk%20that%20sites%20that%20have%20blocked%20the%20company's%20access%20to%20training%20data%20won't%20get%20picked%20up%20in%20AI-generated%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20a%20query%20is%20'What%20is%20the%20best%20deep%20dish%20pizza%20in%20Chicago%3F'%20and%20a%20Pizza%20shop%20excludes%20Google's%20AI%20from%20using%20its%20website%20data%20to%20train%20on%2C%20then%20it%20will%20not%20have%20any%20knowledge%20of%20that%20restaurant%20and%20be%20unable%20to%20include%20it%20in%20its%20response%2C%26quot%3B%20Gillham%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20is%20testing%20an%20early%20version%20of%20genAI%20search%20through%20its%20Search%20Generative%20Experience%2C%20or%20SGE.%20It's%20unclear%20if%20the%20company%20will%20launch%20this%20fully%20in%20the%20future%2C%20or%20how%20much%20different%20it%20will%20be%20from%20the%20traditional%20Google%20search%20engine.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20decisions%20will%20go%20a%20long%20way%20to%20deciding%20the%20future%20of%20the%20web%20in%20this%20new%20AI%20world.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EAxel%20Springer%2C%20Business%20Insider's%20parent%20company%2C%20has%20a%20global%20deal%20to%20allow%20OpenAI%20to%20train%20its%20models%20on%20its%20media%20brands'%20reporting.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fe