A37%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fchuck-schumer-top-jewish-politician-in-us-calls-for-israel-election-and-issues-warning-to-benjamin-netanyahu-13094728%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fchuck-schumer-top-jewish-politician-in-us-calls-for-israel-election-and-issues-warning-to-benjamin-netanyahu-13094728%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fchuck-schumer-top-jewish-politician-in-us-calls-for-israel-election-and-issues-warning-to-benjamin-netanyahu-13094728%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Supreme%20Court%20Rejects%20Manish%20Sisodia's%20Curative%20Petition%20Seeking%20Bail%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20rejected%20Manish%20Sisodia's%20curative%20petition%20challenging%20the%20top%20court%20decision%20rejecting%20his%20bail%20plea%20in%20liquor%20policy%20irregularities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20of%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%2C%20with%20justices%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%2C%20BR%20Gavai%20and%20SVN%20Bhatti%20dismissed%20the%20curative%20petition%20filed%20by%20Manish%20Sisodia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20gone%20through%20the%20Curative%20Petitions%20and%20the%20connected%20documents.%20In%20our%20opinion%2C%20no%20case%20is%20made%20out%20within%20the%20parameters%20indicated%20in%20the%20decision%20of%20this%20Court%20in%20Rupa%20Ashok%20Hurra%20vs%20Ashok%20Hurra%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20top%20court%20said%20in%20its%20March%2013%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Curative%20Petitions%20are%20dismissed%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20top%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20December%2013%2C%20the%20top%20court%20rejected%20former%20Delhi's%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Manish%20Siodia's%20review%20petition%20against%20top%20court%20order%20denying%20him%20bail%20in%20the%20excise%20policy%20irregularities%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20October%2030%202023%20the%20top%20court%20dismissed%20Manish%20Sisodia's%20bail%20plea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20had%20earlier%20noted%20that%20the%20existing%20excise%20policy%20was%20changed%20to%20facilitate%20and%20get%20kickbacks%20and%20bribes%20from%20the%20wholesale%20distributors%20by%20enhancing%20their%20commission%2Ffee%20from%205%20percent%20under%20the%20old%20policy%20to%2012%20percent%20under%20the%20new%20policy.%20Accordingly%2C%20a%20conspiracy%20was%20hatched%20to%20carefully%20draft%20the%20new%20policy%2C%20deviating%20from%20the%20expert%20opinion%2Fviews%20to%20create%20an%20eco-system%20to%20ensure%20unjust%20enrichment%20of%20the%20wholesale%20distributors%20at%20the%20expense%20of%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3Egovernment%20exchequer%20or%20the%20consumer.%20The%20illegal%20income%20(proceeds%20of%20crime%2C%20as%20per%20the%20DoE)%20would%20partly%20be%20recycled%20and%20returned%20in%20the%20form%20of%20bribes%2C%20it%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20probe%20agency%20has%20alleged%20that%20Vijay%20Nair%2C%20who%20was%20the%20middleman%2C%20a%20go-between%2C%20a%20member%20of%20AAP%2C%20and%20a%20co-confident%20of%20the%20appellant%20-%20Manish%20Sisodia%2C%20had%20interacted%20with%20Butchi%20Babu%2C%20Arun%20Pillai%2C%20Abhishek%20Boinpally%20and%20Sarath%20Reddy%2C%20to%20frame%20the%20excise%20policy%20on%20conditions%20and%20terms%20put%20forth%20and%20to%20the%20satisfaction%20and%20desire%20of%20the%20liquor%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20policy%20favoured%20and%20promoted%20cartelisation%20and%20large%20wholesale%20distributors%20with%20high%20market%20share%20because%20of%20extraneous%20reasons%20and%20kickbacks%2C%20were%20ensured%20to%20earn%20exorbitant%20profits%2C%20CBI%20alleged%2C%20which%20was%20noted%20by%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20had%20earlier%20also%20noted%20the%20CBI's%20submission%20that%20the%20excess%20amount%20of%207%20percent%20commission%2Ffee%20earned%20by%20the%20wholesale%20distributors%20of%20Rs.%20338%2C00%2C00%2C000%20(rupees%20three%20hundred%20thirty-eight%20crores%20only)%20constitute%20an%20offence%20as%20defined%20under%20Section%207%20of%20the%20PoC%20Act%2C%20relating%20to%20a%20public%20servant%20being%20bribed.%20(As%20per%20the%20DoE%2C%20these%20are%20proceeds%20of%20crime).%20This%20amount%20was%20earned%20by%20the%20wholesale%20distributors%20in%20a%20span%20of%20ten%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20July%203%2C%202023%2C%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20denied%20him%20bail%20in%20both%20matters%20being%20probed%20by%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20and%20Enforcement%20Directorate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20February%202023%2C%20Manish%20Sisodia%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20CBI%20for%20alleged%20irregularities%20in%20the%20framing%20and%20implementation%20of%20now-scrapped%20Delhi's%20new%20excise%20policy.%20The%20policy%20was%20withdrawn%20amid%20allegations%20of%20foul%20play%20by%20the%20opposition.%20Manish%20Sisodia%20is%20currently%20in%20judicial%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20CBI%2C%20Manish%20Sisodia%20had%20played%20the%20most%20important%20and%20vital%20role%20in%20the%20criminal%20conspiracy%20and%20he%20had%20been%20deeply%20involved%20in%20the%20formulation%20as%20well%20as%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20said%20policy%20to%20ensure%20the%20achievement%20of%20the%20objectives%20of%20the%20said%20conspiracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710440220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-03%2F357b20bs_manish-sisodia-650_625x300_01_March_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-rejects-manish-sisodias-curative-petition-seeking-bail-in-delhi-liquor-policy-scam-5240058%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20rejected%20Manish%20S