2%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Electoral%20Bonds%20Data%20From%20SBI%20Uploaded%20On%20Election%20Commission%20Website%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20big%20move%20towards%20transparency%20in%20political%20funding%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20has%20uploaded%20the%20data%20of%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20given%20to%20it%20by%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India.%20The%20details%20have%20been%20uploaded%20on%20Thursday%2C%20a%20day%20before%20the%20deadline%20set%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20data%20pertains%20to%20purchases%20of%20bonds%20of%20denominations%20between%20Rs%201%2C000%20and%20Rs%201%20crore%20dating%20back%20to%20April%2012%2C%202019%2C%20and%20reveals%20purchases%20by%20companies%20as%20well%20as%20individuals.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20EC's%20website%20has%20two%20lists.%20The%20first%20is%20of%20companies%20that%20purchased%20electoral%20bonds%2C%20along%20with%20the%20denomination%20and%20dates.%20The%20other%20has%20names%20of%20the%20political%20parties%20as%20well%20as%20the%20denominations%20of%20the%20bonds%20and%20the%20dates%20on%20which%20they%20were%20encashed.%20There%20is%2C%20however%2C%20no%20way%20of%20correlating%20the%20lists%20and%20finding%20out%20which%20company%20or%20individual%20had%20donated%20to%20which%20party.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20that%20contributed%20the%20most%20through%20the%20method%20is%20Future%20Gaming%20and%20Hotel%20Services%20PR%2C%20which%20bought%20bonds%20worth%20Rs%201%2C368%20crore.%20Megha%20Engineering%20And%20Infrastructures%20Limited%20was%20second%2C%20purchasing%20bonds%20worth%20Rs%20966%20crore.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20Rs%20410%20crore%2C%20Qwik%20Supply%20Chain%20Private%20Limited%20was%20a%20distant%20third%2C%20followed%20by%20Vedanta%20Limited%20at%20Rs%20400%20crore%20and%20Haldia%20Energy%20Limited%20at%20Rs%20377%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBharti%20Group%20is%20sixth%2C%20having%20donated%20Rs%20247%20crore%2C%20followed%20by%20Essel%20Mining%20And%20Inds%20Ltd%20at%20Rs%20224%20crore.%20The%20remaining%20three%20in%20the%20list%20of%20top%2010%20donors%20are%20Western%20UP%20Power%20Transmission%20Company%20Limited%2C%20which%20contributed%20Rs%20220%20crore%2C%20Keventer%20Foodpark%20Infra%20Ltd%2C%20which%20gave%20Rs%20195%20crore%2C%20and%20Madanlal%20Ltd%20at%20Rs%20185%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20parties%20that%20encashed%20electoral%20bonds%20include%20the%20BJP%2C%20Congress%2C%20Trinamool%20Congress%2C%20AAP%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party%2C%20AIADMK%2C%20BRS%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20TDP%2C%20YSR%20Congress%2C%20DMK%2C%20JDS%2C%20NCP%2C%20JDU%20and%20RJD.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnnouncing%20that%20it%20has%20released%20the%20data%2C%20the%20poll%20body%20said%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20has%20today%20uploaded%20the%20data%20on%20electoral%20bonds%20on%20its%20website%20as%20received%20from%20SBI%20on%20'as%20is%20where%20is%20basis'%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20may%20be%20recalled%20that%20in%20the%20said%20matter%2C%20ECI%20has%20consistently%20and%20categorically%20weighed%20in%20favour%20of%20disclosure%20and%20transparency%2C%20a%20position%20reflected%20in%20the%20proceedings%20of%20the%20Hon'ble%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20noted%20in%20the%20order%20also%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdvocate%20Prashant%20Bhushan%20-%20who%20had%20appeared%20for%20the%20Association%20of%20Democratic%20Reforms%2C%20one%20of%20the%20petitioners%20in%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20case%20-%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20serial%20numbers%20of%20the%20bonds%20were%20not%20mentioned%20in%20the%20data.%20This%2C%20he%20said%2C%20was%20necessary%20to%20figure%20out%20who%20donated%2C%20and%20how%20much%2C%20to%20which%20party.%20He%20also%20claimed%20that%20contributions%20not%20being%20anonymous%20was%20implicit%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Info%20of%20%23ElectoralBonds%20uploaded%20by%20EC%20(which%20they%20say%20is%20as%20recd%20from%20SBI)%2C%20does%20not%20give%20the%20serial%20number%20of%20the%20bonds%2C%20which%20is%20necessary%20for%20finding%20who%20gave%20bond%20to%20whom.%20This%20was%20implicit%20in%20SC%20Jt.%20SBI%20affidavit%20said%20this%20info%20is%20recorded%20though%20in%20separate%20silos%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bhushan%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20Info%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FElectoralBonds%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23ElectoralBonds%3C%2Fa%3E%20uploaded%20by%20EC%20(which%20they%20say%20is%20as%20recd%20from%20SBI)%2C%20does%20not%20give%20the%20serial%20number%20of%20the%20bonds%2C%20which%20is%20necessary%20for%20finding%20who%20gave%20bond%20to%20whom.%20This%20was%20implicit%20in%20SC%20Jt.%20SBI%20affidavit%20said%20this%20info%20is%20recorded%20though%20in%20separate%20silos.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FWTcq0pmDvR%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FWTcq0pmDvR%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Prashant%20Bhushan%20(%40pbhushan1)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fpbhushan1%2Fstatus%2F1768298131836309923%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2014%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20data%20can%20be%20accessed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eci.gov.in%2Fdisclosure-of-electoral-bonds%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESupreme%20Court's%20Warning%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20hearing%20on%20Monday%2C%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20bench%20led%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20DY%20Chandrachud%20had%20come%20down%20heavily%20on%20the%20SBI%20for%20%E2%80%9Cwilful%20disobedience%20of%20its%20order%E2%80%9D%20on%20the%20data%20being%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20poll%20body%20by%20March%206.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20had%20ordered%20the%20SBI%20to%20submit%20the%20data%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20by%20Tuesday%2C%20warning%20it%20of%20contempt%20proceedings%20if%20it%20failed%20to%20do%20so.%20The%20court%20had%20also%20directed%20the%20chairman%20and%20managing%20director%20of%20the%20bank%20to%20file%20an%20affidavit%20after%20the%20order%20had%20been%20complied%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESBI%2C%20which%20is%20India's%20largest%20bank%2C%20had%20submitted%20the%20data%20on%20Tuesday%20and%20filed%20the%20affidavit%20in%20the%20court%20the%20day%20after%20that.%20The%20affidavit%20stated%20that%2022%2C217%20electoral%20bonds%20were%20issued%20between%20April%202019%20and%20February%2015%2C%202024%2C%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20struck%20down%20the%20scheme%20after%20declaring%20it%20unconstitutional%20and%20arbitrary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bank%20said%20political%20parties%20had%20redeemed%2022%2C030%20bonds%20while%20the%20remaining%20187%20were%20redeemed%20and%20the%20money%20was%20deposited%20in%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20national%20relief%20fund%2C%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20will%20hear%20a%20petition%20filed%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission%20on%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20order%20on%20Friday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710438060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F2074em5g_rajasthan-assembly-elections-_625x300_11_October_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felectoral-bonds-data-received-from-sbi-uploaded-on-website-says-election-commission-5238831%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20big%20move%20towards%20transparency%20in%20political%20funding%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20has%20uploaded%20the%20data%20of%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20given%20to%20it%20by%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20on%20Thursday%2C%20a%20day%20before%20the%20deadline%20set%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felectoral-bonds-data-received-from-sbi-uploaded-on-website-says-election-commission-5238831%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felectoral-bonds-data-received-from-sbi-uploaded-on-website-says-election-commission-5238831%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felectoral-bonds-data-received-from-sbi-uploaded-on-website-says-election-commission-5238831%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SpaceX's%20Mega-Rocket%20Starship%20%26quot%3BLost%26quot%3B%20During%20Atmospheric%20Re-Entry%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EStarship%2C%20the%20world's%20most%20powerful%20rocket%2C%20flew%20further%20and%20faster%20than%20ever%20before%20during%20its%20third%20test%20flight%20Thursday%2C%20although%20it%20was%20eventually%20lost%20as%20it%20re-entered%20the%20atmosphere%20over%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%2C%20SpaceX%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELift-off%20from%20the%20company's%20Starbase%20in%20Boca%20Chica%2C%20Texas%20came%20around%208%3A25%20am%20local%20time%20(1325%20GMT)%20and%20was%20carried%20live%20on%20a%20webcast%20that%20was%20watched%20by%20millions%20on%20social%20media%20platform%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sleek%20mega%20rocket%20is%20vital%20to%20NASA's%20plans%20for%20landing%20astronauts%20on%20the%20Moon%20later%20this%20decade%20--%20and%20Elon%20Musk's%20hopes%20of%20colonizing%20Mars%20someday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCongrats%20to%20%40SpaceX%20on%20a%20successful%20test%20flight!%26quot%3B%20tweeted%20NASA%20administrator%20Bill%20Nelson%20following%20the%20test.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20eyes%20were%20on%20Thursday's%20launch%20after%20two%20prior%20attempts%20ended%20in%20spectacular%20explosions.%20But%20that's%20not%20necessarily%20a%20bad%20thing%3A%20The%20company%20has%20adopted%20a%20rapid%20trial-and-error%20approach%20to%20accelerate%20development%2C%20and%20the%20strategy%20has%20brought%20it%20numerous%20successes%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20Objectives%20met%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20two%20stages%20of%20Starship%20are%20combined%2C%20the%20rocket%20stands%20397%20feet%20(121%20meters)%20tall%20--%20beating%20the%20Statue%20of%20Liberty%20by%20a%20comfortable%2090%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20Super%20Heavy%20Booster%20produces%2016.7%20million%20pounds%20(74.3%20Meganewtons)%20of%20thrust%2C%20almost%20double%20that%20of%20the%20world's%20second%20most%20powerful%20rocket%2C%20NASA's%20Space%20Launch%20System%20--%20though%20the%20latter%20is%20now%20certified%2C%20while%20Starship%20is%20still%20a%20prototype.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarship's%20third%20launch%20test%20in%20its%20fully%20stacked%20configuration%20was%20its%20most%20ambitious%20yet%20and%20the%20company%20said%20it%20was%20able%20to%20meet%20many%20of%20its%20objectives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20included%20opening%20and%20closing%20Starship's%20payload%20door%20to%20test%20its%20ability%20to%20deliver%20satellites%20into%20orbit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHigh%20definition%20footage%20from%20an%20onboard%20camera%20showed%20Starship%20coasting%20in%20space%2C%20with%20the%20curve%20of%20the%20Earth%20visible%20in%20the%20background.%20It%20hit%20a%20top%20speed%20of%20more%20than%2026%2C000%20kilometers%20per%20hour%20(16%2C000%20mph)%20and%20achieved%20an%20altitude%20of%20more%20than%20200%20kilometers%20above%20sea%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarship%20flew%20halfway%20around%20the%20globe%2C%20then%20began%20its%20descent%20over%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%2C%20with%20engineers%20cheering%20as%20its%20heat%20shield%20composed%20of%2018%2C000%20hexagonal%20tiles%20glowed%20red%20hot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20ground%20control%20stopped%20receiving%20signals%20and%20announcers%20declared%20the%20vessel%20%26quot%3Blost%26quot%3B%20before%20it%20could%20achieve%20its%20final%20goal%20of%20splashing%20down.%20The%20lower-stage%20booster%20also%20failed%20to%20make%20a%20successful%20water%20landing%2C%20and%20as%20a%20result%2C%20the%20Federal%20Aviation%20Administration%20said%20it%20was%20opening%20a%20%26quot%3Bmishap%26quot%3B%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStarship%20will%20make%20life%20multiplanetary%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%2C%20the%20company's%20billionaire%20founder%2C%20posted%20on%20X%20afterward%2C%20emphasizing%20the%20progress%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20Real%20world%20testing%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20so-called%20%26quot%3Bintegrated%26quot%3B%20test%20came%20in%20April%202023.%20SpaceX%20was%20forced%20to%20blow%20up%20Starship%20within%20a%20few%20minutes%20of%20launch%2C%20because%20the%20two%20stages%20failed%20to%20separate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rocket%20disintegrated%20into%20a%20ball%20of%20fire%20and%20crashed%20into%20the%20Gulf%20of%20Mexico%2C%20sending%20a%20dust%20cloud%20over%20a%20town%20several%20miles%20(kilometers)%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20test%20in%20November%202023%20fared%20slightly%20better%3A%20The%20booster%20separated%20from%20the%20spaceship%2C%20but%20both%20then%20exploded%20over%20the%20ocean%2C%20in%20what%20the%20company%20euphemistically%20called%20a%20%26quot%3Brapid%20unscheduled%20disassembly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20currently%20costs%20SpaceX%20around%20%2490%20million%20to%20build%20each%20Starship%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20by%20the%20research%20company%20Payload%20published%20in%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpaceX's%20strategy%20of%20carrying%20out%20tests%20in%20the%20real%20world%20rather%20than%20in%20labs%20has%20paid%20off%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20Falcon%209%20rockets%20have%20come%20to%20be%20workhorses%20for%20NASA%20and%20the%20commercial%20sector%2C%20its%20Dragon%20capsule%20sends%20astronauts%20and%20cargo%20to%20the%20International%20Space%20Station%2C%20and%20its%20Starlink%20internet%20satellite%20constellation%20now%20covers%20dozens%20of%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20clock%20is%20ticking%20for%20SpaceX%20to%20be%20ready%20for%20NASA's%20planned%20return%20of%20astronauts%20to%20the%20Moon%20in%202026%2C%20using%20a%20modified%20Starship%20as%20the%20lander%20vehicle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20is%20approaching%20in%20the%20rear%20view%20mirror%2C%20targeting%202030%20to%20land%20its%20first%20crew%20on%20the%20Moon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20does%20SpaceX%20need%20to%20prove%20it%20can%20launch%2C%20fly%20and%20land%20Starship%20safely%20--%20it%20must%20eventually%20also%20show%20it%20can%20send%20multiple%20%26quot%3BStarship%20tankers%26quot%3B%20into%20orbit%20to%20refuel%2C%20at%20supercooled%20temperatures%2C%20a%20main%20Starship%20for%20its%20onward%20journey%20to%20the%20Moon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710437820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Facjbpe9g_starship-3rd-test-flight-_625x300_14_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fspacexs-starship-mega-rocket-lost-during-atmospheric-re-entry-5239200%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22SpaceX's%20Starship%20mega-rocket%20was%20%26quot%3Blost%26quot%3B%20during%20re-entry%20through%20Earth's%20atmosphere%20during%20its%20third%20test%20flight%2C%20the%20company%20said%20in%20a%20webcast%20Thursday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fspacexs-starship-mega-rocket-lost-during-atmospheric-re-entry-5239200%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fspacexs-starship-mega-ro