y%20much%20like%20any%20other%20after%20the%20final%20bell%20at%20Kendall%20Central%20School%2C%20collecting%20her%20thoughts%20and%20belongings%20before%20departing%20for%20home.%20Shortly%20after%20she%20sent%20a%20message%20to%20her%20husband%2C%20she%20was%20found%20unconscious%20in%20her%20classroom%2C%20as%20reported%20by%20Matthew%20Smith%2C%20a%20dear%20friend%20of%20the%20couple%2C%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gofundme.com%2Ff%2Fcourtney-and-hadley-fannon%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EGoFundMe%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMrs%20Fannon%2C%20expecting%20her%20first%20daughter%2C%20Hadley%20Jaye%2C%20was%20taken%20to%20a%20nearby%20hospital%2C%20where%20life-saving%20efforts%20began%20for%20both%20mother%20and%20daughter.%20Tragically%2C%20they%20died%20later%20that%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20world%20lost%202%20beautiful%20souls%2C%20Courtney%20Fannon%20and%20Hadley%20Jaye%20Fannon%2C%20long%20before%20we%20were%20ready%20to%20live%20in%20a%20world%20without%20them.%20They%20were%20called%20to%20eternal%20rest%20the%20night%20of%20March%208th%2C%20after%20a%20very%20tragic%20and%20unexpected%20turn%20of%20events%2C%E2%80%9D%20according%20to%20the%20GoFundMe%20post.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20GoFundMe%20campaign%20has%20garnered%20approximately%20%2447%2C623%20as%20of%20Wednesday.%20These%20funds%20will%20be%20allocated%20to%20cover%20various%20final%20expenses%2C%20such%20as%20medical%20bills%2C%20and%20funeral%20service%20costs%2C%20and%20to%20provide%20short-term%20financial%20support%20for%20Mrs%20Fannon's%20husband%2C%20Kurtis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20media%20outlet%20reported%20that%20Mrs%20Fannon%20had%20taught%20special%20education%20in%20the%20district%20since%202018.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCourtney%20was%20a%20special%20education%20teacher%20who%20served%20her%20students%20with%20passion%20and%20joy%20each%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20Schools%20Superintendent%20Nicholas%20Picardo%20said%20in%20a%20message%2C%20USA%20Today%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20she%20wasn't%20in%20her%20classroom%20sharing%20her%20love%20and%20gift%20for%20teaching%20with%20her%20students%2C%20she%20could%20be%20found%20walking%20our%20halls%20with%20a%20smile%20and%20a%20friendly%20hello%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Smith%20in%20his%20lengthy%20post%20on%20GoFundMe%20wrote%20that%20Mr%20Kurtis%20is%20living%20the%20%E2%80%9Cworst%20nightmare%20of%20having%20to%20return%20to%20a%20home%2C%20filled%20with%20baby%20toys%2C%20bottles%2C%20furniture%20and%20a%20finished%20nursery%2C%20that%20will%20no%20longer%20be%20filled%20with%20the%20cooing%20sounds%20and%20shuffling%20of%20a%20newborn.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMrs%20Fannon%20was%20due%20to%20give%20birth%20%E2%80%9Cin%20just%204%20short%20weeks%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20those%20who%20did%20not%20have%20the%20wonderful%20opportunity%20to%20meet%20or%20get%20to%20know%20Courtney%2C%20there%20is%20an%20endless%20amount%20of%20positive%20and%20good%20things%20that%20can%20only%20be%20said%20about%20her%2C%E2%80%9D%20Smith%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CShe%20was%20loving%2C%20genuine%20and%20organized%20in%20a%20way%20that%20always%20placed%20her%20students%20ahead%20of%20herself%2C%20ultimately%20changing%20the%20lives%20of%20her%20students%20and%20caregivers%2C%20always%20for%20the%20positive%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESmith%20also%20addressed%20the%20unborn%20girl%20in%20his%20tribute.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710435120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fohv6ep0g_courtney-fannon_625x300_14_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpregnant-us-teacher-collapses-in-classroom-and-dies-weeks-before-baby-was-due-5239642%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mrs%20Fannon%2C%20expecting%20her%20first%20daughter%2C%20Hadley%20Jaye%2C%20was%20taken%20to%20a%20nearby%20hospital%2C%20whe