th%20Hardik%20Pandya.%20When%20he%20joined%20in%202015%2C%20he%20became%20quite%20the%20rage%20but%20in%202016%20he%20had%20a%20bad%20season.%20The%20thing%20is%20when%20you're%20an%20uncapped%20player%2C%20franchises%20release%20you%20quickly%20and%20then%20assess%20how%20a%20player%20is%20performing%20in%20Ranji%20Trophy%20or%20other%20domestic%20matches%20before%20maybe%20taking%20them%20back.%20But%20Rohit%20did%20not%20let%20it%20happen.%20That's%20why%20these%20guys%20went%20on%20to%20become%20the%20players%20that%20they%20did.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EHe%20also%20talked%20about%20Hardik%20Pandya%20and%20even%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Jos%20Buttler%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1367-jos-buttler-playerprofile%5C%22%3EJos%20Buttler%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20why%20don't%20you%20post%20the%20whole%20statement%3F%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCricCrazyJohns%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40CricCrazyJohns%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F3aEYgOIkgb%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F3aEYgOIkgb%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F2j2bgOoM4J%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F2j2bgOoM4J%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Serah%20(%40Iwillhuntuhdown)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIwillhuntuhdown%2Fstatus%2F1768175104524190043%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2014%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTalking%20about%20international%20players%2C%20I%20can%20talk%20about%20Jos%20Buttler.%20In%20the%202017%20season%2C%20Rohit%20Sharma%20felt%20he%20could%20contribute%20more%20as%20an%20opener.%20So%2C%20Rohit%20Sharma%20demoted%20himself%20and%20I%20opened%20with%20JOs%20Buttler.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanhwile%2C%20Hardik%20Pandya%20expressed%20happiness%20at%20joining%20the%20Mumbai%20Indians%