ng%20the%20stunning%20formation%20born%20from%20aging%20Sun-like%20stars'%20interaction.%20The%20image%20shared%20on%20Instagram%20mesmerized%20viewers%20with%20its%20ethereal%20beauty%20and%20cosmic%20allure.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Science%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fhome%2Fscience%2Fnasa-captures-stunning-necklace-nebula-located-15000-light-years-away%2Farticleshow%2F108500212.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fhome%2Fscience%2Fnasa-captures-stunning-necklace-nebula-located-15000-light-years-away%2Famp_articleshow%2F108500212.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fhome%2Fscience%2Fnasa-captures-stunning-necklace-nebula-located-15000-light-years-away%2Famp_articleshow%2F108500212.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Who%20are%20the%20New%20Election%20Commissioner-Appointees%2C%20Sukhbir%20Singh%20Sandhu%20and%20Gyanesh%20Kumar%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F06152712%2FElection-Commission-of-India-Photo-PTI1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20committee%20headed%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20picked%20two%20retired%20Indian%20Administrative%20Service%20(IAS)%20officers%20%E2%80%93%20Sukhbir%20Singh%20Sandhu%20and%20Gyanesh%20Kumar%20%E2%80%93%20as%20election%20commissioners%20(ECs).%20They%20are%20scheduled%20to%20be%20sworn%20in%20tomorrow%20(March%2015)%2C%20according%20to%20a%20gazette%20notification%20issued%20by%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20meeting%20of%20the%20selection%20committee%20was%20held%20at%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20residence%20on%20Thursday%20(March%2014).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20appointments%20have%20come%20just%20days%20before%20a%20schedule%20for%20the%20general%20elections%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20announced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20contravention%20of%20the%20guidelines%20laid%20down%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20the%20Anoop%20Banarwal%20judgment%20of%20March%202%2C%202023%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fnew-bill-selection-of-election-commissioners%5C%22%3Ewas%20not%20in%20the%20panel%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Instead%2C%20on%20the%20committee%20to%20pick%20two%20ECs%20were%20his%20senior%20party%20colleague%20and%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20and%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20Adhir%20Chowdhury%2C%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20largest%20Opposition%20party%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20minutes%20after%20the%20meeting%20ended%2C%20Choudhury%20stated%20publicly%20that%20he%20was%20neither%20given%20adequate%20time%20to%20look%20at%20the%20profile%20of%20the%20candidates%20for%20the%20post%20nor%20given%20the%20list%20of%20the%20shortlisted%20names.%20The%20entire%20list%20of%20212%20candidates%20was%20handed%20over%20to%20him%20just%20a%20day%20before%20the%20meeting%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEssentially%2C%20it%20implies%20that%20the%20candidates%20were%20shortlisted%20between%20Modi%20and%20Shah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20the%20PM-led%20committee%20announced%20the%20appointment%20of%20the%20ECs%20just%20a%20day%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20was%20to%20hear%20a%20petition%20challenging%20the%20legitimacy%20of%20the%20committee%20itself%20on%20grounds%20of%20its%20stranglehold%20over%20the%20independence%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission%2C%20has%20raised%20questions%20regarding%20the%20urgency%20displayed%20by%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20party%20(BJP)-led%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20ECs%20are%20scheduled%20to%20take%20the%20oath%20tomorrow%20morning%20(March%2015)%2C%20while%20the%20matter%20will%20also%20be%20heard%20on%20the%20same%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20is%20Gyanesh%20Kumar%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20retired%20IAS%20officer%20of%20the%20Kerala%20cadre%2C%20Gyanesh%20Kumar%20belongs%20to%20the%201988%20batch.%20Kumar%20has%20worked%20closely%20with%20Shah%2C%20both%20as%20minister%20of%20home%20affairs%20and%20as%20the%20minister%20of%20cooperatives.%20Kumar%20also%20worked%20as%20the%20parliamentary%20affairs%20secretary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKumar%20has%20been%20the%20key%20person%20for%20a%20number%20of%20significant%20moves%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20had%20embarked%20on%20after%20its%20return%20to%20power%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*As%20joint%20secretary%20of%20the%20Kashmir%20desk%20at%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%2C%20Kumar%20worked%20closely%20with%20Amit%20Shah%20in%20the%20transition%20of%20the%20state%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20into%20a%20Union%20Territory%20in%20August%202019.%20He%20was%20an%20active%20participant%20in%20the%20preparation%20of%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Reorganisation%20Bill%2C%20which%20then%20became%20an%20Act.%20The%20reading%20down%20of%20Article%20370%20was%20the%20first%20massive%20decision%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20took%20after%20its%20return%20to%20power%20in%202019.%20Shah%20became%20the%20home%20minister%20in%202019%20replacing%20Rajnath%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*After%20the%20successful%20completion%20of%20the%20Kashmir%20project%2C%20Kumar%2C%20in%20January%202020%2C%20was%20deputed%20by%20Shah%20to%20the%20Ayodhya%20desk%20at%20the%20MHA.%20As%20the%20head%20of%20this%20desk%2C%20he%20oversaw%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20Trust%20to%20build%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20in%20Ayodhya.%20The%20consecration%20of%20the%20temple%2C%20built%20under%20the%20watch%20of%20that%20Trust%2C%20was%20carried%20out%20by%20Modi%20on%20January%2022%2C%20an%20occasion%20being%20used%20by%20Modi-Shah%20and%20their%20party%20to%20garner%20votes%20in%20the%20ensuing%20general%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*Around%20the%20time%20Modi%20inaugurated%20the%20temple%20at%20Ayodhya%2C%20Kumar%20retired%20from%20service.%20After%20heading%20the%20Ayodhya%20desk%2C%20he%20was%20dispatched%20to%20the%20parliamentary%20affairs%20ministry%20as%20its%20secretary%20in%20April%202021.%20One%20of%20the%20major%20aberrations%20noticed%20during%20that%20period%20in%20parliament%20was%20a%20blanket%20ban%20%E2%80%93%20first%20ever%20%E2%80%93%20on%20journalists%20with%20government%20accreditation%20to%20cover%20the%20sessions.%20It%20was%20also%20the%20time%20the%20Modi%20government%20was%20constructing%20the%20new%20parliament%20building%20and%20the%20Central%20Vista%20area%20as%20a%20symbol%20of%20%E2%80%98Naya%20Bharat%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20time%20Modi%20inaugurated%20the%20new%20parliament%20building%2C%20Kumar%2C%20often%20termed%20as%20one%20of%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20right-hand%20man%20in%20the%20power%20corridors%20of%20Delhi%2C%20was%20sent%20to%20another%20ministry.%20This%20ministry%20is%20also%20headed%20by%20Shah%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Cooperation.%20In%20May%202022%2C%20Kumar%20became%20secretary%2C%20Ministry%20of%20Cooperation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20retiring%20from%20service%20in%20January%2C%20Kumar%20had%20put%20together%20three%20cooperative%20societies%20within%20the%20ministry%2C%20a%20flagship%20project%20of%20the%20Modi%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20his%20tenure%2C%20the%20cooperation%20ministry%20saw%20enactment%20of%20the%20Multi-State%20Cooperative%20Societies%20(MSCS)%20(Amendment)%20Act%2C%202023%2C%20and%20formation%20of%20three%20new%20national%20cooperative%20bodies%20%E2%80%94%20Bharatiya%20Beej%20Sahakari%20Samiti%20Limited%20(BBSSL)%2C%20National%20Cooperative%20Organics%20Limited%20(NCOL)%2C%20and%20National%20Cooperative%20Export%20Limited%20(NCEL).%20He%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20the%20timely%20launch%20of%20the%20CRCS-Sahara%20refund%20portal%20for%20submission%20of%20claims%20by%20genuine%20depositors%20of%20four%20Multi-State%20Cooperative%20Societies%20of%20Sahara%20Group%2C%E2%80%9D%20wrote%20the%3Cem%3E%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20after%20the%20news%20spread%20about%20his%20name%20as%20one%20of%20the%20election%20commissioners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20a%20day%20before%20Kumar%20was%20reportedly%20picked%20by%20the%20committee%20to%20the%20post%2C%20Shah%20inaugurated%20a%20new%20office%20to%20unroll%20the%20work%20that%20was%20to%20be%20carried%20out%20under%20those%20cooperative%20societies.%20He%20called%20them%20a%20panacea%20to%20%E2%80%9Csolve%20many%20problems%20of%20Indian%20agriculture%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20they%20would%20%E2%80%9Cenhance%20farmers%E2%80%99%20income%20by%20promoting%20exports%20of%20farm%20products%2C%20including%20organic%20foods.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Press%20Information%20Bureau%20note%20said%2C%20while%20inaugurating%20the%20office%2C%20%E2%80%9CShah%20mentioned%20that%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Shri%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20we%20are%20moving%20ahead%20with%20the%20vision%20of%20%E2%80%98Sahakar%20se%20Samriddhi%E2%80%99.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20is%20S.S.%20Sandhu%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESandhu%2C%20another%20retired%20IAS%20officer%20from%20the%201988%20batch%2C%20happens%20to%20be%20a%20batchmate%20of%20Kumar%2C%20from%20the%20Uttarakhand%20cadre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20being%20sent%20back%20to%20Uttarakhand%20to%20take%20over%20as%20the%20chief%20secretary%20in%20July%202021%2C%20Sandhu%20was%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20National%20Highways%20Authority%20of%20India%20(NHAI).%20He%20took%20over%20the%20reins%20of%20the%20NHAI%20in%20October%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESandhu%20was%20instrumental%20in%20carrying%20out%20some%20of%20the%20key%20road%20projects%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%2C%20including%20constructing%20a%20record%20number%20of%20highways.%20This%20accomplishment%20of%20NHAI%20under%20Sandhu%20has%20been%20a%20key%20party%20campaign%20highlight.%20Modi%20has%20been%20seen%20inaugurating%20highways%20to%20showcase%20that%20the%20NHAI%E2%80%99s%20achievement%20is%20actually%20because%20of%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESandhu%20was%20to%20retire%20as%20Uttarakhand%20chief%20secretary%20in%20July%202023.%20However%2C%20he%20was%20given%20a%20six-month%20extension%20because%20of%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20ongoing%20works%20at%20Kedarnath%20and%20Badrinath%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20number%20of%20key%20projects%20funded%20by%20the%20Centre%20that%20are%20underway%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%2C%20as%20per%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fdehradun%2Fchief-secy-ss-sandhu-gets-6-month-extension%2Farticleshow%2F102027337.cms%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ETimes%20of%20India.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20projects%20around%20the%20Hindu%20pilgrimage%20sites%20of%20Badrinath%20and%20Kedarnath%20have%20been%20one%20of%20the%20flagship%20initiatives%20of%20the%20Modi%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.narendramodi.in%2Fprime-minister-narendra-modi-to-visit-kedarnath-and-badrinath-on-21st-october-565210%5C%22%3Evisit%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Badrinath%20and%20Kedarnath%20in%20October%202021%20to%20launch%20those%20projects%20made%20headlines.%20Sandhu%20oversaw%20those%20projects%20at%20the%20state%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710427429000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F06152712%2FElection-Commission-of-India-Photo-PTI1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fwho-are-the-new-election-commissioner-appointees-sukhbir-singh-sandhu-and-gyanesh-kumar%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kumar%20and%20Sandhu%20are%20retired%20IAS%20batchmates.%20Kumar%20has%20been%20key%20to%20several%20home%20ministry%20projects%20and%20also%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20Trust.%20Before%20being%20sent%20back%20to%20Uttarakhand%20to%20take%20over%20as%20the%20chief%20secretary%20in%20July%202021%2C%20Sandhu%20was%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20NHAI.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fwho-are-the-new-election-commissioner-appointees-sukhbir-singh-sandhu-and-gyanesh-kumar%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SpaceX%20launches%20its%20mammoth%20Starship%20rocket%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710427203000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FD130%2Fproduction%2F_132925535_p0hjn1jl.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fscience-environment-68565986%233%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20most%20powerful%20rocket%20system%20ever%20built%20lifted%20off%20from%20its%20base%20in%20southeast%20Texas.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A60%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fav%2Fscience-environment-68565986%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Amanda%20Cerny%20showers%20love%20on%20Jacqueline%20Fernandez%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710427133000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108498809%2Cimgsize-36138.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Famanda-cerny-showers-love-on-jacqueline-fernandez-says-says-shes-obsessed-with-her-latest-music-video-yimmy-yimmy-see-post%2Farticleshow%2F108498809.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F108498809.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EAmanda%20Cerny%20praised%20Jacqueline%20Fernandez's%20song%20%26quot%3BYimmy%20Yimmy%26quot%3B%20on%20Instagram%2C%20with%20Jacqueline%20reciprocating%20the%20love.%20The%20song%2C%20a%20remake%20of%20Tayc's%20%26quot%3BN%E2%80%99y%20pense%20plus%2C%26quot%3B%20is%20a%20collaboration%20between%20Shreya%20Ghoshal%20and%20Jacqueline.%20Jacqueline%20is%20also%20busy%20filming%20the%20comedy%20%26quot%3BWelcome%20to%20the%20Jungle%2C%26quot%3B%20set%20for%20release%20on%20December%2020%2C%202024.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Famanda-cerny-showers-love-on-jacqueline-fernandez-says-says-shes-obsessed-with-her-latest-music-video-yimmy-yimmy-see-post%2Farticleshow%2F108498809.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Vehicle%20Thefts%20In%20India%20Saw%202.5%20Times%20Spike%20In%202023.%20Delhi%20Tops%20The%20Chart%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EVehicle%20thefts%20in%20India%20witnessed%20a%20spike%20of%202.5%20times%20in%202023%2C%20compared%20to%202022%2C%20with%20the%20national%20capital%20topping%20the%20chart.%20As%20per%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.acko.com%2Freports%2Facko-theft-and-city-report-2024%2F%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Theft%20%26amp%3B%20the%20City%202024'%20report%20by%20Acko%20Digital%20Insurance%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%2080%20per%20cent%20of%20car%20thefts%20in%20the%20country%20happen%20in%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CNew%20Delhi%20continues%20to%20be%20the%20reigning%20city%20for%20vehicle%20thefts%2C%20with%2080%25%20of%20car%20thefts%20in%20India%20happening%20in%20New%20Delhi%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20revealed%20that%20the%20national%20capital%20witnessed%20a%20vehicle%20theft%20every%2014%20minutes%2C%20resulting%20in%20105%20cases%20each%20day%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20report%20claimed%20that%20there%20is%20progress%2C%20as%20the%20cases%20in%20Delhi%20have%20come%20down%20to%2037%20per%20cent%20in%202023%20from%2056%20per%20cent%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20stated%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20capital%20continues%20to%20be%20the%20hub%20for%20vehicle%20theft%20in%20India%2C%20with%20105%20cases%20of%20vehicle%20theft%20reported%20every%20single%20day%20in%202023.%20To%20put%20that%20into%20perspective%20a%20vehicle%20is%20stolen%20every%2014%20minutes%20in%20the%20capital.%20However%2C%20its%20overall%20share%20of%20vehicle%20thefts%20in%20comparison%20to%20other%20cities%20in%20India%20has%20come%20down%20from%2056%25%20to%2037%25.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20is%20followed%20by%20Chennai%2C%20which%20has%20recorded%20a%20sharp%20spike%20in%202023%2C%20taking%20the%20second%20spot%20on%20the%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CChennai%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20has%20seen%20a%20sharp%20spike%2C%20with%20vehicle%20thefts%20doubling%20from%205%25%20in%202022%20to%2010.5%25%20in%202023.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20the%20second%20spot%20was%20occupied%20by%20Bengaluru%2C%20which%20is%20in%20third%20place%20in%20the%20chart.%20However%2C%20in%202023%2C%20Bengaluru%20has%20also%20recorded%20a%20marginal%20rise%20at%2010.2%20per%20cent%20compared%20to%209%20per%20cent%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CBengaluru%20comes%20a%20close%20third%20at%2010.2%25%2C%20a%20marginal%20increase%20from%209%25%20in%202022.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20must%20be%20noted%20that%20cities%20like%20Kolkata%2C%20Hyderabad%20and%20Mumbai%20have%20registered%20the%20lowest%20number%20of%20thefts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20most%20stolen%20car%2C%20the%20report%20highlighted%20that%2047%20per%20cent%20of%20all%20stolen%20cars%20are%20Maruti%20Wagon%20R%2C%20followed%20by%20Maruti%20Swift%2C%20Hyundai%20Creta%2C%20Hyundai%20Grand%20i10%2C%20and%20Maruti%20Swift%20Dzire.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710427080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F0or8anec_suv-generic-suvs-generic-istock_625x300_18_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvehicle-theft-in-india-see-rise-of