s%2C%20was%20on%20Thursday%20granted%20a%20third-party%20application%20provider%20license%20by%20the%20country's%20payments%20authority%2C%20which%20will%20enable%20it%20to%20facilitate%20payments%20after%20its%20banking%20unit%20ceases%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20license%20will%20allow%20customers%20to%20continue%20using%20the%20Paytm%20app%20for%20payments%20through%20India's%20popular%20unified%20payment%20interface%20(UPI)%2C%20after%20Paytm%20Payments%20Bank%20ceases%20operations%20by%20March%2015%2C%20following%20regulatory%20action%20due%20to%20non-compliance%20with%20certain%20norms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAxis%20Bank%2C%20HDFC%20Bank%2C%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20and%20Yes%20Bank%20will%20act%20as%20payment%20system%20provider%20banks%20to%20Paytm%2C%20the%20National%20Payments%20Corporation%20of%20India%20(NPCI)%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%20Bank%20shall%20also%20act%20as%20a%20merchant%20acquiring%20bank%20for%20existing%20and%20new%20UPI%20merchants%20for%20Paytm%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPaytm%20has%20been%20advised%20to%20complete%20the%20migration%20for%20all%20existing%20handles%20and%20mandates%2C%20wherever%20required%2C%20to%20new%20payment%20system%20provider%20banks%20at%20the%20earliest%2C%20the%20NPCI%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUPI%20is%20India's%20real-time%20payments%20system%20that%20allows%20users%20to%20transfer%20money%20across%20banks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPaytm%2C%20the%20third-largest%20app%20for%20UPI%20payments%20in%20the%20country%2C%20processed%201.41%20billion%20monthly%20transactions%20worth%201.65%20trillion%20rupees%20in%20February%2C%20down%20from%201.57%20billion%20transactions%20worth%201.93%20trillion%20in%20January%2C%20according%20to%20data%20on%20the%20NPCI%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPhonePe%20and%20Google%20Pay%20are%20the%20two%20largest%20UPI%20payment%20apps%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20(RBI)%20had%20asked%20the%20NPCI%20to%20examine%20a%20request%20from%20Paytm%20to%20become%20a%20third-party%20application%20provider.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarly%20this%20week%2C%20Reuters%20was%20the%20first%20to%20report%20that%20the%20NCPI%20was%20likely%20to%20approve%20a%20third-party%20application%20provider%20(TPAP)%20license%20for%20Paytm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710426660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fgttnbha8_paytm-reuters_625x300_16_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpaytm-gets-third-party-app-license-from-payments-authority-5238460%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20National%20Payments%20Corporation%20of%20India%20on%20Thursday%20said%20it%20granted%20digital%20payments%20firm%20Paytm%20a%20third-party%20application%20provider%20license.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpaytm-gets-third-party-app-license-from-payments-authority-5238460%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpaytm-gets-third-party-app-license-from-payments-authority-5238460%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpaytm-gets-third-party-app-license-from-payments-authority-5238460%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Modi's%20Viksit%20Bharat%20May%20Not%20Cut%20it%20in%20the%20Elections%20So%20the%20BJP%20turns%20to%20Polarisation%20Again%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12175557%2FScreenshot-2024-03-12-at-5.55.44-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EThis%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theindiacable.com%2Fp%2Fmaharashtra-on-renaming-spree-modis%5C%22%3Epiece%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0was%20first%20published%20on%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%3EThe%20India%20Cable%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%93%C2%A0a%20premium%20newsletter%20from%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3EThe%20Wire%3Ci%3E%20%26amp%3B%20Galileo%20Ideas%20%E2%80%93%20and%20has%20been%20republished%20here.%20To%20subscribe%20to%20The%20India%20Cable%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theindiacable.com%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3Eclick%20here%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20series%20of%20episodes%20over%20the%20last%20month%20in%20which%20the%20BJP%20has%20had%20to%20face%20reverses%20have%20now%20forced%20it%20to%20play%20its%20most%20consistent%20card%20at%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sudden%20notification%20of%20the%20controversial%20Citizenship%20(Amendment)%20Rules%20by%20the%20Amit%20Shah-led%20Union%20home%20ministry%2C%20even%20as%20over%20200%20petitions%20challenging%20the%20constitutionality%20of%20the%20Citizenship%20(Amendment)%20Act%2C%202019%20are%20under%20judicial%20scanner%2C%20suggests%20in%20no%20uncertain%20terms%20that%20the%20BJP%20will%20lapse%20into%20its%20polarising%20tactics%20once%20again%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20%E2%80%93%20even%20as%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20promises%20a%20%E2%80%9CViksit%20Bharat%E2%80%9D%20by%202047.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah%E2%80%99s%20ministry%20sat%20on%20the%20CAA%20rules%20for%20over%20five%20years%20but%20decided%20to%20notify%20it%20tactically%20on%20the%20first%20day%20of%20Ramzan%2C%20when%20the%20Muslims%20come%20together%20to%20celebrate%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20holy%20month.%20The%20divisive%20nature%20of%20the%20CAA%20that%20upends%20the%20secular%20definition%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20citizenship%20law%20had%20triggered%20widespread%20protests%20by%20the%20Muslim%20community%20and%20a%20large%20section%20of%20democratic-minded%20citizens.%20The%20protests%20were%20communalised%20day%20and%20night%20by%20the%20top%20BJP%20leaders%20to%20target%20Indian%20Muslims.%20The%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20notification%20of%20the%20rules%20now%20is%20clearly%20aimed%20at%20stoking%20hate%20for%20Muslims%2C%20and%20consolidating%20support%20for%20the%20BJP%20within%20India%E2%80%99s%20Hindu%20community%20along%20sectarian%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20religious%20polarisation%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20enough%2C%20the%20BJP%20in%20Haryana%20has%20decided%20to%20polarise%20the%20Haryana%20electorate%20along%20caste%20lines.%20This%20week%20saw%20the%20replacement%20of%20the%20unpopular%20Haryana%20chief%20minister%20Manohar%20Lal%20Khattar%20with%20an%20OBC%20face%20%E2%80%93%20Nayab%20Singh%20Saini.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12142049%2Fimage-1933.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22826%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12142049%2Fimage-1933.png%20826w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12142049%2Fimage-1933-300x167.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-701241%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22460%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EKurukshetra%20MP%20Nayab%20Singh%20Saini.%20Photo%3A%20X%40mr_mayank%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20failure%20of%20seat-sharing%20talks%20with%20its%20ally%20Jannayak%20Janta%20Party%20(JJP)%2C%20and%20dissent%20by%20a%20few%20prominent%20BJP%20Jat%20leaders%20against%20Khattar%E2%80%99s%20leadership%2C%20was%20taken%20as%20an%20opportunity%20to%20drive%20its%20anti-Jat%20rhetoric%20and%20consolidate%20OBC%20caste%20groups%2C%20which%20incidentally%20form%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20electorate.%20The%20BJP%20rode%20to%20power%20in%20Haryana%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%202014%20by%20polarising%20non-Jat%20groups%20against%20the%20dominant%20Jat%20peasantry.%20It%20anointed%20the%20little-known%20Khattar%2C%20a%20loyal%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20foot%20soldier%20belonging%20to%20the%20Bania%20community%2C%20as%20the%20chief%20minister%20but%20was%20forced%20to%20partner%20with%20the%20Jat-dominated%20JJP%20to%20muster%20a%20majority%20in%20the%20assembly.%20The%20saffron%20party%20used%20its%20anti-Jat%20political%20rhetoric%20only%20sparingly%20in%20the%20intermittent%20years%2C%20until%20it%20decided%20finally%20to%20drive%20out%20the%20JJP%20from%20the%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20forcing%20the%20JJP%20into%20the%20opposition%20space%2C%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20has%20been%20facing%20farmers%E2%80%99%20anger%20in%20the%20state%20because%20of%20policies%20widely%20seen%20as%20anti-farmer%2C%20now%20looks%20to%20divide%20the%20dominant%20Jat%20votes%20and%20emerge%20as%20the%20sole%20representative%20of%20OBCs%2C%20Dalits%20and%20other%20non-Jat%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECrucially%2C%20the%20polarising%20moves%20made%20by%20the%20BJP%20come%20at%20a%20time%20when%20it%20has%20faced%20a%20series%20of%20setbacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20its%20fervent%20advocacy%20in%20favour%20of%20electoral%20bonds%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20rejected%20the%20anonymous%20political%20funding%20scheme%20as%20%E2%80%9Cunconstitutional%E2%80%9D.%20The%20apex%20court%E2%80%99s%20order%20has%20now%20made%20the%20BJP%20vulnerable%20as%20it%20received%20the%20maximum%20donations%20through%20electoral%20bonds%20in%20the%20time%20the%20scheme%20existed.%20The%20list%20of%20corporate%20donors%2C%20once%20out%2C%20will%20embolden%20the%20opposition%E2%80%99s%20allegation%20that%20cronyism%20has%20flourished%20like%20never%20before%20during%20the%20Modi%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Union%20minister%20Anant%20Kumar%20Hegde%E2%80%99s%20recent%20statement%20that%20the%20BJP%20wants%20a%20two-third%20majority%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20to%20%E2%80%9Cchange%20the%20constitution%E2%80%9D