20only%20added%20fuel%20to%20the%20suspicions%20around%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20neutrality%2C%20especially%20after%20the%20Modi%20government%20passed%20a%20law%20to%20oust%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20from%20the%20selection%20process%20of%20election%20commissioners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EObsessed%20with%20managing%20news%20headlines%2C%20especially%20in%20such%20adverse%20situations%2C%20the%20Modi-led%20BJP%20has%20reverted%20to%20playing%20the%20polarisation%20game.%20However%2C%20such%20cynicism%20may%20only%20end%20up%20undermining%20its%20%E2%80%9CViksit%20Bharat%E2%80%9D%20campaign%20and%20revealing%20the%20chinks%20in%20its%20armour.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710426590000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12175557%2FScreenshot-2024-03-12-at-5.55.44-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmodis-viksit-bharat-may-not-cut-it-in-the-elections-so-the-bjp-turns-to-polarisation-again%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Obsessed%20with%20managing%20news%20headlines%2C%20especially%20in%20such%20adverse%20situations%2C%20the%20Modi-led%20BJP%20has%20reverted%20to%20playing%20the%20polarisation%20game.%20However%2C%20such%20cynicism%20may%20only%20end%20up%20undermining%20its%20%E2%80%9CViksit%20Bharat%E2%80%9D%20campaign%20and%20revealing%20the%20chinks%20in%20its%20armour.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmodis-viksit-bharat-may-not-cut-it-in-the-elections-so-the-bjp-turns-to-polarisation-again%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Delhi%20High%20Court%20Dismisses%20Bloomberg's%20Appeal%20Against%20ZEE%20Entertainment%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20on%20Thursday%20upheld%20a%20trial%20court's%20order%20directing%20Bloomberg%20Television%20Production%20Services%20India%20Pvt%20Ltd%20(Bloomberg)%20to%20take%20down%20the%20defamatory%20article%20dated%20February%2021%20published%20against%20ZEE%20Entertainment%20Enterprises%20Ltd%20(ZEE)%20relating%20to%20the%20corporate%20governance%20and%20business%20operations%20of%20the%20latter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditional%20District%20Judge%20(ADJ)%20Harjyot%20Singh%20Bhalla%2C%20in%20relief%20to%20ZEE%2C%20had%20held%20that%20it%20had%20made%20out%20a%20prima%20facie%20case%20for%20passing%20ad%20interim%20ex-parte%20orders%20of%20injunction%20and%20directed%20Bloomberg%20to%20take%20down%20the%20defamatory%20article%20from%20its%20platform%20within%20one%20week%20of%20receipt%20of%20the%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBloomberg%20had%2C%20last%20week%2C%20moved%20the%20high%20court%20against%20the%20ADJ's%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Shalinder%20Kaur%2C%20who%20presided%20over%20the%20case%2C%20dismissed%20Bloomberg's%20appeal%20and%20granted%20three%20days'%20time%20to%20comply%20with%20the%20directions%20of%20the%20ADJ.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trial%20court%20had%20restrained%20Bloomberg%20from%20posting%2C%20circulating%2C%20or%20publishing%20the%20article%20on%20any%20online%20or%20offline%20platform%20till%20the%20next%20date%20of%20hearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZEE%2C%20in%20its%20suit%2C%20argued%20that%20the%20Bloomberg%20article%20which%20mentioned%20details%20relating%20to%20the%20corporate%20governance%20and%20business%20operations%20of%20ZEE%2C%20were%20inaccurate%20in%20nature%20and%20led%20to%20a%2015%20per%20cent%20drop%20in%20share%20price%20of%20the%20company%2C%20eroding%20investor%20wealth.%20It%20said%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bfalse%20and%20factually%20incorrect%26quot%3B%20article%20was%20published%2C%20with%20a%20pre-meditated%20and%20mala%20fide%20intention%20to%20defame%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20article%2C%20it%20said%2C%20incorrectly%20published%20that%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Board%20of%20India%20(SEBI)%20has%20found%20a%20%24241%20million%20accounting%20issue%20at%20t