20between%202%2C600%20and%202%2C800%20MLD%2C%20or%20million%20litres%20per%20day.%20At%20present%2C%20however%2C%20there%20is%20a%20shortfall%20of%20more%20than%201%2C500%20MLD.%20And%20it%20isn't%20just%20the%20state%20capital%3B%20nearly%20240%20taluks%20have%20been%20declared%20as%20'drought-hit'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shivakumar%2C%20whose%20government%20has%20said%20it%20is%20working%20to%20address%20the%20shortfall%20and%20ensure%20equitable%20and%20reasonably%20priced%20access%20for%20all%2C%20today%20insisted%20the%20problem%20isn't%20as%20bad%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20far%20as%20Bengaluru%20goes%2C%20there%20is%20no%20water%20crisis.%20Around%207%2C000%20bore-wells%20have%20dried%20up%20but%20we%20have%20made%20arrangements%20for%20all%20that.%20We%20have%20taken%20over%20tankers.%20We%20have%20identified%20the%20water%20sources...%20we%20will%20see%20that%20water%20is%20supplied%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shivakumar's%20statement%2C%20however%2C%20has%20not%20gone%20down%20well%20with%20the%20opposition%20BJP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party's%20state%20unit%20chief%2C%20BY%20Vijayendra%2C%20has%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20ruling%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBeing%20a%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20a%20responsible%20Minister%2C%20is%20it%20not%20his%20responsibility%20to%20address%20the%20water%20issue%20for%20the%20entire%20state%3F%20It%20is%20a%20totally%20unfortunate%20attitude...%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENDTV%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20spoke%20to%20a%20few%20students%20from%20the%20city%2C%20who%20also%20seemed%20to%20disagree%2C%20and%20pointed%20out%20that%20even%20if%20there%20is%20no%20%26quot%3Bcrisis%26quot%3B%20today%2C%20there%20will%20be%20one%20when%20summer%20peaks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20student%2C%20from%20Bengaluru's%20Banaswadi%20area%2C%20said%20people%20there%20have%20been%20facing%20an%20acute%20problem%20for%20the%20past%20week.%20%26quot%3BWe%20relied%20on%20water%20tankers%20and%20that%20was%20expensive...%20Rs%202%2C500%20to%20Rs%203%2C000%20per%20tanker.%20This%20is%20completely%20unaffordable%20for%20normal%20families%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20second%20said%20that%20while%20there%20may%20not%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Blarge-scale%20crisis%26quot%3B%20today%2C%20%26quot%3B...%20government%20should%20intervene%2C%20because%20next%20month%20will%20be%20hotter%20and%20water%20needs%20will%20increase.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20had%20a%20sharp%20message%20to%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP%2C%20who%20have%20predictably%20jumped%20to%20blame%20games.%20%26quot%3BPolitics%20should%20be%20out%20of%20water%20supply.%20When%20there%20is%20a%20water%20crisis%2C%20then%20politicians%20should%20work%20together%20instead%20of%20criticising%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20this%20comes%20days%20after%20city%20authorities%20announced%20fines%20for%20misuse%20or%20wastage%20of%20drinking%20water.%20Residents%20were%20warned%20against%20using%20potable%20water%20for%20washing%20vehicles%2C%20in%20construction%20activities%2C%20or%20at%20cinema%20halls%20and%20shopping%20malls%2C%20except%20for%20drinking%20purposes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbangalore-news%2Fbengaluru-water-crisis-penalty-for-bengaluru-residents-using-water-for-washing-cars-construction-5199048%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStop%20Misusing%20Drinking%20Water%20In%20Bengaluru%20Or%20Pay%20Rs%205%2C000%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20penalty%20of%20Rs%205%2C000%20will%20be%20imposed%20on%20first-time%20violators%20and%20repeat%20offenders%20will%20be%20fined%20an%20extra%20Rs%20500%20each%20time%2C%20the%20Bengaluru%20Water%20Supply%20and%20Sewerage%20Board%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBengaluru%20residents%20-%20whose%20days%20now%20revolve%20around%20worrying%20about%20depleting%20water%20levels%20at%20home%20and%20arranging%20for%20the%20next%20tanker%20-%20have%20welcomed%20the%20imposition%20of%20fines%2C%20but%20stressed%20that%20the%20final%20problem%20is%20still%20the%20lack%20of%20any%20water%20supply.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20these%20fines%20are%20necessary...%20because%20there%20are%20people%20who%20waste%20water%20still.%20But%2C%20in%20the%20end%2C%20we%20need%20water.%20If%20water%20is%20there%2C%20then%20fines%20can%20be%20issued.%20If%20water%20is%20not%20there%2C%20then%20what%20is%20the%20use%20of%20fines%3F%26quot%3B%20Sibi%20Verghese%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Bengaluru's%20Babusapalya%2C%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbangalore-news%2Fbengaluru-water-crisis-bengaluru-residents-hospitals-cry-for-help-as-water-reserves-dwindle-5229006%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E'Don't%20Work-From-Home%2C%20Go%20Home'%3A%20Water%20Crisis%20In%20Bengaluru%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20being%20India's%20'Silicon%20City'%2C%20has%20also%20rolled%20out%20mobile%20phone%20apps%20to%20help%20deal%20with%20this%20crisis.%20These%20are%20Jala%20Mitra%20(for%20citizens%2C%20retired%20technical%20staff%2C%20and%20NGOs%20willing%20to%20volunteer%20for%20water%20leakage%2C%20survey%20and%20conservation%20measures)%20and%20Parisara%20Jalasnehi%20(which%20reserves%20supply%20of%20reused%20water%20for%20treated%20purposes%20other%20than%20drinking).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20there%20is%20Antharajala%2C%20which%20allows%20citizens%20to%20apply%20for%20permission%20to%20dig%20bore-wells%2C%20and%20Samrakshaka%2C%20in%20which%20those%20wasting%20drinking%20water%20can%20be%20red-flagged%20to%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20isn't%20just%20homes%20that%20have%20been%20affected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20crisis%20has%20hit%20hospitals%20too.%20Brookfield%20Hospital%20near%20Whitefield%2C%20one%20of%20the%20city's%20poshest%20neighbourhoods%20and%20worst-affected%2C%20depends%20on%20water%20tankers%20and%20needs%2024%2C000%20litres%20every%20three%20days%3B%20this%20is%20apart%20from%205%2C000%20litres%20needed%20daily%20for%20dialysis%20patients.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Pradeep%20Kumar%2C%20a%20medical%20officer%20in%20the%20hospital%2C%20told%20NDTV%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20recycling%20water%20and%20using%20it%2C%20with%20regular%20water%2C%20for%20washing%20and%20cleaning.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Fchannel%2F0029Va4lixw7z4kcvZI9JM12%5C%22%3EClick%20on%20the%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20all%20the%20latest%20updates%20from%20NDTV%20on%20your%20chat.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710425940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F6ilnoii8_bengaluru-water-crisis_625x300_13_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fcities%2Fno-water-crisis-in-bengaluru-dk-shivakumar-irresponsible-bjp-fumes-5238696%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22There%20is%20%26quot%3Bno%20water%20crisis%26quot%3B%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20Karnataka%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20DK%20Shivakumar%20said%20Thursday%2C%20even%20as%20he%20flagged%20off%20auto-rickshaws%20laden%20with%20hoardings%20to%20spread%20awareness%20about%20water%20conservation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fcities%2Fno-water-crisis-in-bengaluru-dk-shivakumar-irresponsible-bjp-fumes-5238696%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fcities%2Fno-water-crisis-in-bengaluru-dk-shivakumar-irresponsible-bjp-fumes-5238696%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fcities%2Fno-water-crisis-in-bengaluru-dk-shivakumar-irresponsible-bjp-fumes-5238696%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Lullabies%20to%20Languages%3A%20Fellowship%20Offers%20Funds%20to%20Help%20Tribal%20Youth%20Preserve%20Generational%20Wisdom%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20has%20been%20published%20in%20partnership%20with%20Samvaad%20%E2%80%93%20Enabled%20by%20Tata%20Steel%20Foundation%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%2050%20years%2C%20India%20has%20lost%20over%20250%20languages%2C%20as%20reported%20by%20UNESCO.%20This%20loss%20not%20only%20affects%20languages%20but%20also%20various%20fields%20like%20history%2C%20biology%2C%20and%20anthropology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20good%20news.%20Lately%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20been%20a%20growing%20effort%20to%20preserve%20cultural%20identities%20throughout%20India%2C%20and%20the%20Samvaad%20Fellowship%20programme%20stands%20as%20a%20significant%20contributor%20to%20this%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarted%20in%202017%20to%20empower%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F344574%2Ftata-samvaad-tribal-conclave-preserves-lost-heritage-artisans-sell-handicrafts%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etribal%20communities%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20fellowship%20encourages%20their%20youth%20to%20document%20their%20history%2C%20culture%2C%20ecology%2C%20traditions%2C%20art%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20purpose%20of%20the%20fellowship%20is%20to%20get%20tribal%20communities%20to%20deep%20dive%20into%20their%20culture%20and%20help%20them%20shape%20their%20ideas%20in%20collaboration%20with%20various%20experts.%20The%20idea%20behind%20documenting%20different%20cultures%20is%20to%20create%20a%20repository%20of%20information%20and%20make%20it%20accessible%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world.%20At%20Samvaad%2C%20being%20a%20tribal%20is%20a%20source%20of%20pride.%20The%20community%20answers%20the%20toughest%20questions%20about%20their%20identity%20and%20tries%20to%20address%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sourav%20Roy%2C%20TSF%20CEO%2C%20told%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fellowship%20is%20part%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F344526%2Fsamvaad-tata-steel-foundation-celebrates-culture-of-tribes-of-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESamvaad%2C%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20biggest%20tribal%20conclaves%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20country%2C%20enabled%20by%20Tata%20Steel%20Foundation%20(TSF).%20It%20takes%20place%20from%2015%20to%2019%20November%20every%20year%20to%20commemorate%20the%20birth%20anniversary%20of%20Birsa%20Munda%2C%20a%20tribal%20independence%20activist%20and%20leader%20from%20Jharkhand%E2%80%99s%20Munda%20tribe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamvaad%20stepped%20into%20a%20decadal%20journey%20in%202023%20and%20the%20recent%20edition%E2%80%99s%20theme%20was%20%E2%80%98Walk%20with%20Me%E2%80%99.%20The%20theme%20recognised%20the%20journey%20of%20ideas%2C%20dialogues%2C%20individuals%2C%20and%20collectives%20within%20and%20among%20the%20tribes%20of%20India%2C%20aiming%20to%20address%20future%20challenges%20through%20shared%20wisdom%2C%20idea%20exchange%2C%20and%20self-learning.%20The%20five-day%20conclave%20spotlighted%20various%20solution-driven%20dialogues%20and%20initiatives%20that%20have%20emerged%20from%20past%20conclaves.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20hosted%20at%20five%20locations%20%E2%80%94%20TSF%20Community%20Hall%20(RD%20Bhatta)%2C%20Jamshedpur%20Nature%20Trail%2C%20Tribal%20Cultural%20Centre%2C%20Gopal%20Maidan%2C%20and%20Johar%20Haat.%20Gopal%20Maidan%20and%20Tribal%20Culture%20Centre%20served%20as%20the%20main%20activity%20hubs%20while%20Johar%20Haat%20housed%20a%20cloud%20kitchen%20facility%20for%20preparing%20food%20for%20home%20delivery%20in%20collaboration%20with%20Zomato.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20the%20conclave%20has%20celebrated%20and%20united%20over%2040%2C000%20people%20from%20over%20200%20tribes%20in%20India%20and%2017%20other%20countries.%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20spoke%20to%20past%20fellows%20%E2%80%94%20Banwang%20Losu%20and%20Amabel%20Susngi%20%E2%80%94%20about%20their%20tremendous%20action%20towards%20preserving%20their%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FWancho_language_training_of_teacher_PC_banwang_losu-1710425245.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20fellowship%20aims%20to%20engage%20tribal%20communities%20in%20exploring%20their%20culture%20and%20collaboratively%20shaping%20their%20ideas%20with%20experts.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FWancho_language_training_of_teacher_PC_banwang_losu-1710425245.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FWancho_language_training_of_teacher_PC_banwang_losu-1710425245-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FWancho_language_training_of_teacher_PC_banwang_losu-1710425245-500x281.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FWancho_language_training_of_teacher_PC_banwang_losu-1710425245-768x432.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FWancho_language_training_of_teacher_PC_banwang_losu-1710425245-150x84.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-344889%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20fellowship%20aims%20to%20engage%20tribal%20communities%20in%20exploring%20their%20culture%20and%20collaboratively%20shaping%20their%20ideas%20with%20experts.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPreserving%20lullabies%20and%20languages%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20centuries%2C%20people%20across%20the%20world%20have%20followed%20the%20nightly%20ritual%20of%20singing%20lullabies%20to%20infants%20for%20a%20peaceful%20sleep.%20Closer%20home%2C%20we%20have%20thousands%20of%20lullabies%20in%20different%20languages.%20However%2C%20this%20tradition%20has%20faded%20over%20the%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsk%20yourself%20whether%20you%20remember%20a%20lullaby%20from%20your%20childhood!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%2028-year-old%20Amabel%20Susngi%20from%20Meghalaya%20observed%20that%20the%20lullabies%20in%20her%20native%20language%20Khasi%20were%20becoming%20a%20thing%20of%20the%20past%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20document%20them.%20As%20part%20of%20the%20Samvaad%20Fellowship%2C%20she%20gathered%20various%20lullabies%20and%20published%20them%20in%20a%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20PhD%20researcher%20and%20a%20singer%2C%20she%20travelled%20across%20Meghalaya%20for%20over%20a%20year%20to%20collect%20these%20lullabies.%20She%20has%20documented%2025%20of%20them%20in%20her%20book%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EHa%20Yupiam%20Ka%20Bei%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20(On%20Mother%E2%80%99s%20Lap)%2C%20which%20was%20published%20in%20both%20Khasi%20and%20English%20this%20year%20at%20Samvaad.%20It%20also%20comes%20with%20musical%20notations%2C%20and%20each%20piece%20has%20a%20QR%20code%20leading%20the%20reader%20to%20its%20YouTube%20version.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20researching%20the%20folk%20music%20of%20the%20Pnar%20community%2C%20I%20realised%20that%20not%20many%20people%20remembered%20lullabies.%20That%20was%20a%20shock.%20Lullabies%20have%20been%20passed%20down%20through%20generations.%20Whether%20traditional%20or%20something%20made%20up%20by%20parents%2C%20it%20has%20been%20an%20important%20fabric%20of%20one%E2%80%99s%20culture%2C%E2%80%9D%20Amabel%20told%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20road%20to%20publishing%20had%20its%20challenges%2C%20she%20adds%2C%20the%20biggest%20being%20research.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CParents%20don%E2%80%99t%20sing%20anymore%2C%20and%20elderly%20people%20do%20not%20quite%20remember%20all%20the%20lullabies.%20Some%20knew%20only%20one%20line%20or%20two%2C%20and%20some%20remembered%20only%20the%20tune%20or%20lyrics.%20Scheduling%20meetings%20was%20not%20an%20option%2C%20so%20I%20had%20to%20work%20around%20their%20availability.%20Samvaad%20solved%20the%20critical%20funding%20problem%2C%20and%20it%20helped%20me%20connect%20with%20other%20fellows%20around%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Banwang%20Losu%20from%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20developed%20a%20script%20to%20preserve%20Wancho%20%E2%80%94%20a%20Tibetan-Burman%20language%20spoken%20in%20the%20Longding%20region%20of%20the%20state%20and%20some%20parts%20of%20Myanmar%2C%20Nagaland%2C%20and%20Assam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBanwang%20first%20felt%20the%20need%20to%20have%20a%20Wancho%20script%20when%20he%20was%20asked%20to%20collect%20data%20about%20his%20community%20as%20part%20of%20his%20socio-economic%20study%20in%20college.%20He%20was%20unable%20to%20find%20the%20right%20English%20words%20to%20convey%20subtle%20tones.%20He%20tried%20to%20do%20some%20research%20and%20even%20started%20pursuing%20a%20master%E2%80%99s%20in%20linguistics%20at%20Deccan%20College%20Post%20Graduation%20and%20Research%20Institute%20in%20Pune.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20developing%20the%20script%2C%20he%20took%20inspiration%20from%20nature%20and%20Wancho%20cultural%20symbols%2C%20practices%2C%20and%20gestures.%20He%20developed%20a%20script%20with%2044%20letters%20(15%20vowels%20and%2029%20consonants)%2C%20each%20letter%20representing%20a%20distinct%20tone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBanwang%20was%20the%20first%20fellow%20at%20Samvaad.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20working%20on%20the%20Wancho%20script%2C%20I%20heard%20about%20Samvaad%20and%20came%20here%20in%202017%20without%20any%20proposal.%20However%2C%20the%20jury%20was%20delighted%20to%20see%20my%20work.%20Being%20a%20fellow%20here%20was%20eye-opening%20as%20it%20is%20the%20only%20programme%20for%20tribals%20at%20this%20scale.%20Using%20the%20grant%2C%20I%20made%20textbooks%20on%20the%20Wancho%20language%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBanwang%20taught%20the%20language%20to%202%2C000%20people%2C%20and%2020%20of%20them%20are%20now%20teachers.%20Thanks%20to%20his%20work%2C%20over%206%2C000%20students%20can%20read%20and%20write%20in%20Wancho.%20He%20also%20got%20the%20script%20approved%20for%20online%20use%20by%20the%20US-based%20Unicode%20Consortium.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%20language%20is%20equally%20important%20irrespective%20of%20how%20big%20or%20small.%20We%20have%20to%20look%20at%20other%20minority%20languages%20with%20the%20same%20status%20and%20build%20scripts%20to%20preserve%20them.%20Loss%20of%20language%20is%20a%20loss%20of%20our%20own%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202560px)%20100vw%2C%202560px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSourav_Roy_taking_a_session_with_fellowship_applicants_11zon-1710425242-scaled.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22This%20year%2C%20out%20of%2035%20applicants%2C%2010%20were%20awarded%20the%20fellowship%20following%20thorough%20rounds%20of%20interviews%20and%20pitches.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSourav_Roy_taking_a_session_with_fellowship_applicants_11zon-1710425242-scaled.jpg%202560w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSourav_Roy_taking_a_session_with_fellowship_applicants_11zon-1710425242-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSourav_Roy_taking_a_session_with_fellowship_applicants_11zon-1710425242-500x281.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSourav_Roy_taking_a_session_with_fellowship_applicants_11zon-1710