in%20conducting%20the%20polls%2C%20even%20as%20the%20latter%20has%20been%20passing%20the%20buck%20on%20the%20former%20with%20respect%20to%20elections%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20delay%20on%20our%20part%3A%20ECI%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClaiming%20that%20there%20was%20no%20delay%20on%20their%20part%20in%20holding%20the%20electoral%20exercise%2C%20the%20CEC%20said%20that%20there%20was%20a%20dissonance%20between%20the%20JandK%20Reorganisation%20Act%2C%202019%20and%20the%20delimitation%20exercise%20completed%20in%202022.%20%C2%A0%E2%80%9CThe%20two%20were%20to%20be%20made%20harmonious%20and%20that%20was%20done%20only%20in%20December%202023%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kumar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CEC%20referred%20to%20the%20changes%20like%20increase%20in%20assembly%20seats%2C%20reservation%20of%20seats%20for%20Scheduled%20Tribes%2C%20reservation%20of%20two%20seats%20for%20Kashmiri%20migrants%20and%20one%20seat%20for%20refugees%20from%20the%20Pakistan%20Occupied%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20which%20were%20to%20be%20incorporated%20in%20the%20Representation%20of%20The%20Peoples%20Act%20and%20the%20Reorganisation%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwed-high-hopes-of-meeting-the-pm-say-kashmiris-who-werent-allowed-to-enter-the-stadium%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98We%E2%80%99d%20High%20Hopes%20of%20Meeting%20the%20PM%2C%E2%80%99%20Say%20Kashmiris%20Who%20Weren%E2%80%99t%20Allowed%20to%20Enter%20the%20Stadium%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Reorganisation%20Act%2C%20after%20the%20acceptance%20of%20the%20Delimitation%20Commission%20(report)%20was%20changed%20in%20December%202023.%20This%20is%20March%2C%202024.%20We%20had%20just%20three%20months.%20So%2C%20there%20is%20no%20delay%20on%20our%20part%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kumar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CEC%E2%80%99s%20claim%20raises%20questions%20on%20why%20the%20Union%20government%20took%2017%20months%20to%20amend%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Reorganisation%20Act%20to%20incorporate%20the%20changes%20necessitated%20by%20the%20delimitation%20exercise%20in%20the%20Reorganisation%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20delimitation%20exercise%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleasePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1822939%5C%22%3Ecompleted%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20May%205%2C%202022.%20%C2%A0In%20July%202023%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20brought%20a%20bill%20in%20the%20Parliament%20to%20make%20the%20delimitation%20exercise%20compatible%20with%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Reorganisation%20Act%2C%202019.%20The%20bill%20was%20cleared%20by%20both%20the%20houses%20of%20the%20Parliament%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleaseIframePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1983311%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAfter%2520discussion%252C%2520the%2520Lok%2520Sabha%2Cthe%2520objectives%2520of%2520the%2520bill.%5C%22%3EDecember%202023%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20post-delimitation%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20and%20the%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janta%20Party%20(BJP)%20have%20been%20repeatedly%20saying%20that%20the%20ECI%20would%20decide%20on%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20polls.%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20Manoj%20Sinha%20has%20also%20made%20similar%20claims%20in%20the%20past%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKumar%2C%20however%2C%20continued%20suspense%20over%20holding%20of%20the%20assembly%20polls%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20decision%20regarding%20holding%20assembly%20polls%20together%20with%20parliamentary%20elections%20or%20at%20an%20interval%20would%20be%20made%20after%20taking%20into%20account%20inputs%20of%20political%20parties%20and%20security%20considerations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJammu%20and%20Kashmir%20saw%20the%20last%20assembly%20election%20in%202014%20and%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20is%20under%20direct%20control%20of%20Union%20government%20since%20June%2019%2C%202018%20when%20BJP%20withdrew%20support%20to%20the%20Mehbooba%20Mufti-led%20government%2C%20citing%20%E2%80%9Cdeteriorating%E2%80%9D%20security%20situation%20in%20the%20then%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20delay%20in%20holding%20assembly%20polls%20has%20left%20the%20people%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20without%20an%20elected%20government%20for%20the%20past%20six%20years.%20Four%20seats%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20are%20also%20vacant%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%20due%20to%20the%20delay%20in%20holding%20assembly%20polls%20in%20the%20Union%20Territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20directed%20the%20ECI%20to%20hold%20the%20exercise%20by%20September%2030%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDirect%20elections%20to%20the%20legislative%20assemblies%20which%20is%20one%20of%20the%20paramount%20features%20of%20representative%20democracy%20in%20India%20cannot%20be%20put%20on%20hold%20until%20statehood%20is%20restored.%20We%20direct%20that%20steps%20shall%20be%20taken%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20to%20conduct%20elections%20to%20the%20legislative%20assembly%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20constituted%20under%20Section%2014%20of%20the%20Reorganisation%20Act%20by%2030%20September%202024%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20five-judge%20constitution%20bench%20led%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%2C%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Fjudiciary%2Fculmination-of-integration-sc-upholds-abrogation-of-article-370-that-gave-jk-special-status%2F1880334%2F%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20its%20verdict%20in%20the%20Article%20370%20case%20on%20December%2011%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710421200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F10152019%2F27423964742_c550b3b390_k.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fis-the-eci-and-union-govt-passing-the-buck-on-jammu-and-kashmir-polls-post-delimitation%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Interestingly%2C%20post-delimitation%2C%20t