isonment%20term%20of%20up%20to%20two%20years%20and%20a%20fine%20of%20around%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20for%20violations.%20Repeat%20offences%20escalate%20to%20a%20five-year%20imprisonment%20term%20and%20a%20fine%20of%20approximately%20Rs%2050%20lakh.%20The%20government%20has%20committed%20to%20investigating%20allegations%20and%20proposing%20appropriate%20actions.%20Strengthening%20advertising%20regulations%20for%20both%20Ayurvedic%20and%20over-the-counter%20(OTC)%20allopathic%20drugs%20should%20be%20a%20priority%20in%20this%20regard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20operate%20in%20grey%20areas.%20For%20instance%2C%20DOMA%20does%20not%20recognise%20a%20list%20of%20drugs%20for%20which%20any%20advertisement%20is%20prohibited.%20But%20that%20still%20leaves%20the%20field%20dangerously%20open%20for%20all%20manner%20of%20products%2C%20including%20some%20vaccines.%20As%20for%20advertisements%20for%20ayurvedic%20products%2C%20these%20are%20more%20common%20than%20their%20allopathic%20counterparts%20because%20they%20do%20not%20require%20pre-approval%20or%20any%20stipulation%20of%20minimum%20information%20for%20the%20consumer.%20Indians%20who%20struggle%20with%20medical%20expenses%20are%20particularly%20vulnerable%20to%20the%20growing%20promotion%20of%20an%20%E2%80%9Cindigenous%E2%80%9D%20medical%20system%20supposedly%20offering%20cheaper%20remedies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPatanjali%E2%80%99s%20prosperity%20and%20its%20ability%20to%20evade%20legal%20scrutiny%20highlight%20a%20troubling%20issue%3A%20the%20lack%20of%20accessible%20and%20affordable%20healthcare.%20The%20underprivileged%20find%20themselves%20trapped%2C%20facing%20a%20choice%20between%20enduring%20delayed%20treatment%20from%20conventional%20medicine%20or%20falling%20victim%20to%20misleading%20and%20exploitative%20advertising%2C%20exacerbating%20their%20plight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeceptive%20advertisements%20not%20only%20breach%20legal%20standards%20but%20also%20endanger%20public%20health%20by%20disseminating%20misinformation%20about%20evidence-based%20treatments%20and%20targeting%20vulnerable%20individuals.%20Patanjali%E2%80%99s%20misleading%20advertising%20practices%20are%20acknowledged%20as%20a%20critical%20public%20health%20concern%20demanding%20urgent%20intervention.%20The%20recent%20Supreme%20Court%20ruling%20represents%20a%20positive%20initial%20move%20towards%20overhauling%20the%20regulations%20overseeing%20this%20medical%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EShivanand%20Pandit%20is%20an%20autonomous%20finance%20and%20tax%20adviser.%20He%20has%2028%20years%20of%20experience%20in%20finance%2C%20accounting%2C%20taxation%20laws%2C%20cost%20management%2C%20wealth%20management%2C%20audit%2C%20corporate%20and%20banking%20laws.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710414008000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2F09164656%2Framdev.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fopinion%2Ftaken-india-for-a-ride-why-supreme-courts-order-against-patanjali-is-a-significant-step%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indians%20who%20struggle%20with%20medical%20expenses%20are%20particularly%20vulnerable%20to%20the%20growing%20promotion%20of%20an%20%E2%80%9Cindigenous%E2%80%9D%20medical%20system%20supposedly%20offering%20cheaper%20remedies.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fopinion%2Ftaken-india-for-a-ride-why-supreme-courts-order-against-patanjali-is-a-significant-step%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Amit%20Shah%20Dodges%20Question%20of%20'Chronology'%20between%20CAA%20and%20NRC%2C%20Invokes%20'Akhand%20Bharat'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F08123425%2FUntitled-design-5-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EAmit%20Shah%20ducked%20the%20question%20of%20CAA-NRC%20chronology%20which%20had%20fuelled%20one%20of%20the%20widest%20prot