JanataParty%5C%22%3EShah%20shied%20away%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20speaking%20about%20the%20sequence%20of%20CAA%20leading%20to%20the%20NRC.%20Dodging%20the%20question%20on%20chronology%2C%20that%20his%20forceful%20mentions%20had%20pushed%20into%20political%20folklore%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20NRC%20now%2C%20talk%20only%20about%20the%20CAA.%E2%80%9D%20He%20asked%20ANI%20to%20not%20%E2%80%9Cmix%E2%80%9D%20the%20two%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CAkhand%20Bharat%E2%80%9D%20logic%20for%20CAA%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20podcast%20out%20earlier%20today%2C%20Shah%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20Akhand%20Bharat%2C%20all%20the%20religious%20minorities%20who%20had%20been%20persecuted%2C%20we%20have%20a%20duty%20to%20protect%20and%20offer%20refuge%20to.%E2%80%9D%20On%20Muslim%20groups%20like%20Hazaras%2C%20Shias%20or%20Ahmadiyas%20being%20possibly%20persecuted%20in%20those%20countries%2C%20Shah%20refused%20to%20accept%20that%20they%20were%20persecuted%2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CAfghanistan%2C%20Pakistan%20and%20Bangladesh%20are%20Islamic%20countries.%20We%20have%20no%20data%20on%20the%20persecution.%20How%20can%20Muslims%20be%20persecuted%20there%3F%E2%80%9D%20Calling%20the%20law%20as%20one%20tied%20with%20India%E2%80%99s%20past%2C%20Shah%20said%20Muslims%20were%20allowed%20to%20seek%20citizenship%20under%20other%20laws%2C%20but%20the%20CAA%20fast-tracked%20citizenship%20for%20non-Muslim%20minorities%20from%20three%20countries%20in%20South%20Asia%20who%20had%20come%20into%20the%20country%20before%20December%202019%20and%20had%20been%20residing%20in%20India%20for%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah%20hastened%20to%20castigate%20the%20Opposition%20for%20raising%20the%20question%20of%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20rules%2C%20as%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Cpart%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20election%20manifesto%20in%202019%20and%20passed%20over%20four%20years%20ago.%E2%80%9D%20The%20rules%20were%20not%20formalised%20due%20to%20%E2%80%9Csome%20political%20complications%2C%20then%20Covid%E2%80%9D.%20He%20insisted%20this%20was%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20about%20political%20gain.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMindful%20of%20the%20chaos%20in%20eastern%20India%2C%20especially%20Assam%2C%20West%20Bengal%20and%20other%20north-eastern%20states%2C%20he%20spoke%20of%20the%20Act%20not%20being%20applicable%20to%20those%20in%20states%20requiring%20Inner%20Line%20Permits%20or%20those%20groups%2Fareas%20protected%20by%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20Sixth%20schedule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20explanatory%20post%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%2C%20%3Cem%3EAltNews%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98s%20Abhishek%20writes%20about%20the%20misrepresentation%2C%20twisting%20of%20facts%20and%20the%20spread%20of%20misinformation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHome%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20said%20that%20in%201951%2C%20Hindu%20Population%20of%20Bangladesh%20was%2022%25.%20You%20must%20be%20thinking%20that%20Bangladesh%20got%20independence%20in%201971%2C%20how%20is%20he%20claiming%20the%20census%20according%20to%201951%3F%20But%20wait%2C%20he%20is%20referring%20to%20East%20Bengal%2FEast%20Pakistan%20(now%20Bangladesh).%20Separate%20data%20is%20available%20for%20East%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20census.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20wait%2C%20when%20he%20claims%20about%20the%20Hindu%20and%20Sikh%20population%20(23%25)%20of%20Pakistan%2C%20the%20point%20must%20be%20noted%2C%20according%20to%20the%20same%20data%20he%20is%20referring%2C%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20first%201951%20census%20data%20available%20on%20the%20Indian%20government%20website%20(pdf%20link%20attached%20below)%2C%20the%20combined%20Hindu%20and%20other%20religion%E2%80%99s%20population%20(excluding%20Muslim%20and%20Christians)%20was%2012.86%25%20of%20the%20total%20Pakistan%2C%20East%20Bengal%2FEast%20Pakistan%20(now%20Bangladesh)%20and%20West%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20data%20of%20East%20Bengal%2FEast%20Pakistan%20(now%20Bangladesh)%20gets%20excluded%20from%20the%20total%20population%20count%2C%20as%20the%20Home%20Minister%20has%20already%20mentioned%20that%20data%20separately%2C%20the%20total%20percentage%20of%20Hindu%20and%20other%20religions%20population%20(excluding%20Muslim%20and%20Christians)%20were%207.5%25%20of%20the%20total%20Population%20of%20today%E2%80%99s%20Pakistan%20(including%20just%20Pakistan%20and%20West%20Pakistan).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20both%20ways%2C%20whether%20he%20includes%20or%20excludes%20East%20Pakistan%20(now%20Bangladesh)%20data%2C%20his%20claim%20about%20the%20post-partition%20census%20is%20still%20incorrect%20about%20the%20Hindu%20and%20Sikh%20population%20in%20Pakistan.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThis%20is%20what%20misrepresentation%20of%20facts%20looks%20like.%20A%20very%20clever%20way%20of%20twisting%20facts%20and%20spreading%20misinformation%20as%20per%20your%20need.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHome%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20said%20that%20in%201951%2C%20Hindu%20Population%20of%20Bangladesh%20was%2022%25.%20You%20must%20be%20thinking%20that%20Bangladesh%20got%20independence%20in%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FLlqmIo79Go%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FLlqmIo79Go%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FQeB4DPBnkt%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FQeB4DPBnkt%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Abhishek%20(%40AbhishekSay)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAbhishekSay%2Fstatus%2F1768208512856035493%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2014%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CHindu%20law%20is%20civil%20code%20only%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah%20also%20spoke%20about%20other%20promises%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%20that%20they%20were%20%E2%80%9Cfulfilling%E2%80%9D.%20In%20answer%20to%20a%20question%2C%20he%20wanted%20%E2%80%9Cforeign%20journalists%E2