%22%3E1.%20Supriyo%20Ranjan%20Mahapatra%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202015%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F247534%2Fodisha-consumer-complaint-amazon-supriyo-lawyer-law-student-laptop-cancelled-asus-customer-care-how-to-information-vid01%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elawyer%20Supriyo%3C%2Fa%3E%20filed%20a%20consumer%20complaint%20against%20Amazon%20after%20his%20confirmed%20order%20was%20cancelled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Supriyo%20found%20a%20laptop%20priced%20at%20Rs%20190%20after%20a%20big%20discount%20of%20Rs%2023%2C309%2C%20he%20quickly%20ordered%20it.%20But%20shortly%20after%2C%20Amazon%20cancelled%20his%20order%2C%20leaving%20him%20frustrated%20with%20their%20customer%20service.%20Determined%20to%20resolve%20the%20issue%2C%20he%20took%20legal%20action.%20His%20efforts%20paid%20off%20three%20years%20later%20when%20he%20was%20awarded%20Rs%2045%2C000%20for%20unfair%20practices%20and%20poor%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20urges%20consumers%20not%20to%20give%20up%20on%20issues%20that%20they%20feel%20strongly%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIssuing%20a%20legal%20notice%20must%20be%20the%20first%20step%2C%20and%20if%20the%20matter%20does%20not%20get%20resolved%2C%20then%20filing%20a%20case%20with%20the%20consumer%20forum%20should%20be%20the%20next%20logical%20step.%20Make%20use%20of%20the%20legislation%20that%20is%20pro-consumers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20advises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fconsumer-rights-1710338115.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lawyer%20Supriyo%20Ranjan%20Mahapatra%20(left)%20and%20police%20officer%20Bhaskar%20Jadhav.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fconsumer-rights-1710338115.jpg%201200w%2