plaints%20with%20the%20Consumer%20Disputes%20Redressal%20Commissions%20(CDRCs)%20if%20they%20are%20being%20charged%20more%20than%20the%20MRP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20the%20District%20Commissioner%20Disputes%20Redressal%20Forum%20directed%20Mumbai-based%20Shagun%20Veg%20Restaurant%20to%20pay%20a%20fine%20of%20Rs%202%20lakh%2C%20pay%20Rs%2010%2C000%20to%20Bhaskar%20as%20compensation%20for%20%E2%80%98mental%20torture%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20refund%20the%20extra%20charge%20of%20Rs%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E3.%20Rohit%20Patel%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%20was%20charged%20Rs%20164%20for%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F246864%2Fhow-to-consumer-rights-court-case-ahmedabad-mrp-over-extra-overcharging-bottled-water-india-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebottle%20of%20water%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20was%20actually%20priced%20at%20Rs%2020.%20He%20filed%20a%20case%20against%20the%20hotel%20at%20the%20Ahmedabad%20(Rural)%20Consumer%20Disputes%20Redressal%20under%20the%20Consumer%20Protection%20Act%2C%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20charged%20150%2B%20taxes.%20When%20I%20asked%20the%20manager%2C%20he%20said%20the%20additional%20charge%20was%20a%20service%20charge%20and%20service%20tax.%20I%20found%20their%20arguments%20ridiculous%20so%20I%20warned%20them%20about%20going%20to%20the%20Consumer%20Forum%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202015%2C%20he%20went%20to%20the%20forum%2C%20made%20an%20affidavit%2C%20filled%20out%20a%20complaint%20form%2C%20and%20kept%20his%20evidence%20%E2%80%94%20the%20bottle%20and%20the%20hotel%20bill%2C%20ready.%20Once%20his%20complaint%20was%20approved%2C%20a%20legal%20notice%20was%20sent%20to%20the%20hotel%20and%20the%20proceedings%20required%20Rohit%20to%20appear%20in%20court%2028%20times!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Rohit%20did%20not%20give%20up%2C%20and%20after%20a%20five-year-long%20legal%