also%20passing%20on%20her%20skills%20to%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlong%20with%20telling%20the%20families%20in%20our%20village%20why%20Oraon%20paintings%20are%20important%2C%20I%20also%20tell%20them%20the%20financial%20perks%20and%20recognitions%20that%20come%20with%20it.%20I%20share%20with%20them%20the%20reasons%20why%20we%20have%20been%20making%20profits.%20I%20tell%20them%20that%20people%2C%20who%20have%20never%20heard%20about%20our%20tribe%2C%20like%20what%20we%20make!%20And%20it%20can%20be%20a%20lucrative%20career%20option.%20Several%20families%20are%20now%20either%20passing%20on%20the%20skills%20to%20their%20kids%20themselves%20or%20sending%20them%20to%20me%20for%20classes%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamvaad%20is%20a%20large%20gathering%20that%20includes%20over%20200%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F335418%2Fphotos-of-unique-tribes-in-the-world-by-trupal-pandya-photographer-brokpa-ladakh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etribal%20communities%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20brings%20together%20more%20than%202%2C500%20people%20to%20celebrate%20tribal%20identity%2C%20art%2C%20healing%20practices%2C%20and%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%20courtesy%3A%20Samvaad%20by%20Tata%20Steel%20Foundation)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710339160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_0999_11zon-1710330407.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D344734%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tata%20Samvaad%20in%20Jamshedpur%20provided%20artisan%20Sumanti%20Devi%20a%20platform%20for%20showcasing%20Oraon%20art.%20Through%20workshops%2C%20networking%2C%20and%20sales%20opportunities%2C%20she%20highlighted%20her%20community%E2%80%99s%20heritage%20while%20learning%20new%20skills%20and%20connecting%20with%20experts.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Gopi%20Kare